e brands\\\", allowing you to choose only the benefits (such as luggage, change, and cancellation terms) you need, thus saving money on unnecessary extras.\",\"url\":\"https://www.cryptorefills.com/en/flights#step3\",\"image\":\"https://cryptorefills.s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/images/book-flight-with-bitcoin-step3a.gif\"},{\"@type\":\"HowToStep\",\"name\":\"Step 4: Pay with crypto\",\"text\":\"At checkout, choose your preferred cryptocurrency as the payment method. Cryptorefills accepts a range of cryptocurrencies including USDT, USDC, and other stablecoins. Simply complete the transaction and you're all set!\",\"url\":\"https://www.cryptorefills.com/en/flights#step4\",\"image\":\"https://cryptorefills.s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/images/book-flight-with-bitcoin-step4.gif\"},{\"@type\":\"HowToStep\",\"name\":\"Step 5: Receive your ticket\",\"text\":\"Once your payment is confirmed, you'll receive your flight ticket via email.\",\"url\":\"https://www.cryptorefills.com/en/flights#step5\",\"image\":\"https://cryptorefills.s3-eu-west-1.amazonaws.com/images/book-flight-with-bitcoin-step5.jpg\"}]}"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"30:Te3a,"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\"mainEntity\":[{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How do flight bookings work on Cryptorefills?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Cryptorefills uses a fully IATA and ARC accredited flight provider, Duffel to provide you with a seamless flight booking experience.  When you choose to book a flight through Cryptorefills, Duffel's API connects you to a wide range of airlines and flight options, allowing you to search, book, and manage your flights directly from our platform.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Which cryptocurrencies can be used to pay for flights?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"You can pay for your booking with all the cryptocurrencies and wallets that we support. The only exception is BTC payments on the mainnet, due to the short expiration times associated with flight bookings. This ensures faster transaction processing and reduces the risk of price fluctuations affecting your booking.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Can I make changes to my flight?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"In some cases yes, you can make changes to your flight bookings*. To do so, log into your Cryptorefills account or create one using the email address you provided during your booking. Navigate to your order history, and from there, you can initiate a chat with a Duffel support agent to request changes to your flight. *Please note that not all bookings can be changed, pay particular attention to the order change policy when selecting a flight if you think you'll need to make changes. Modifiying a booking may incur a fee, in accordance with the terms and conditions of the booking.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Can I pay for flight changes with cryptocurrency?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"No, fees related to flight bookings (such as change fees or additional charges) must be paid in fiat currency. This policy ensures that the processing of changes is handled smoothly and efficiently.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"How secure are my transactions and personal information?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Cryptorefills and Duffel prioritize the security of your transactions and personal information. Both platforms use advanced encryption and security measures to protect your data. Additionally, using cryptocurrencies for payment can offer an extra layer of security and privacy.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Can I book international flights with crypto?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"Yes! You can book flights to and from any country where airlines are available on the Duffel platform. Cryptorefills supports global flight bookings with cryptocurrency, making it easy to pay for international travel with Bitcoin, USDT, USDC, and other cryptocurrencies.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"Do I need an account to book a flight?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"You don't need a Cryptorefills account to book a flight. However, creating an account allows you to track your orders and manage future bookings more easily. If you book without an account, we'll send your flight confirmation to the email address you provide during checkout.\"}},{\"@type\":\"Question\",\"name\":\"What happens if my flight is cancelled?\",\"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\":\"If your flight is cancelled by the airline, you'll be entitled to a refund or rebooking according to the airline's policy and applicable regulations. Changes and refunds are managed through Duffel support. Please note that refunds for flight cancellations must be processed in fiat currency, in accordance with standard airline policies.\"}}]}"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"26:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"w-full \",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"script\",\"howto-jsonld\",{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$2f\"}}],[\"$\",\"script\",\"faq-jsonld\",{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"$30\"}}],\"$L31\",\"$L32\",\"$L33\",\"$L34\",\"$L35\",\"$L36\"]}]\n31:[\"$\",\"script\",\"service-jsonld\",{\"type\":\"application/ld+json\",\"dangerouslySetInnerHTML\":{\"__html\":\"{\\\"@context\\\":\\\"https://schema.org\\\",\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Service\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Book and Pay for Flights with Cryptocurrency\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Search and book flights from hundreds of airlines and pay with Bitcoin, Ethereum, USDT, USDC, and other cryptocurrencies via Cryptorefills.\\\",\\\"provider\\\":{\\\"@type\\\":\\\"Organization\\\",\\\"name\\\":\\\"Cryptorefills\\\",\\\"url\\\":\\\"https://www.cryptorefills.com\\\"},\\\"areaServed\\\":\\\"Worldwide\\\",