d States\",\"uy\":\"Uruguay\",\"uz\":\"Uzbekistan\",\"va\":\"Vatican City\",\"vc\":\"Saint Vincent and the Grenadines\",\"ve\":\"Venezuela\",\"vg\":\"Virgin Islands (British)\",\"vi\":\"Virgin Islands (U.S.)\",\"vn\":\"Vietnam\",\"vu\":\"Vanuatu\",\"wf\":\"Wallis and Futuna\",\"ws\":\"Samoa\",\"xk\":\"Kosovo\",\"ye\":\"Yemen\",\"yt\":\"Mayotte\",\"za\":\"South Africa\",\"zm\":\"Zambia\",\"zw\":\"Zimbabwe\",\"ww\":\"Global\",\"asia\":\"Asia\",\"eu\":\"Europe\"},\"x_country_iso_code\":\"US\"}]}],\"$L50\",\"$L51\",\"$L52\"]\n"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"36:[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mx-auto my-16 w-full max-w-(--breakpoint-2xl) p-3\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex flex-col justify-between gap-x-20 lg:flex-row lg:px-0\",\"children\":[[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"flex flex-col\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"h2\",null,{\"className\":\"mb-1 text-2xl font-semibold sm:text-4xl md:max-w-sm md:leading-snug dark:text-gray-100\",\"children\":\"Frequently asked questions\"}]}],[\"$\",\"div\",null,{\"className\":\"mt-6 flex w-full flex-col items-center text-gray-600 sm:rounded-2xl md:max-w-4xl\",\"children\":[\"$\",\"$L53\",null,{\"faqQuestions\":[{\"subject\":\"Flights\",\"questions\":[{\"subject\":\"Flights\",\"question\":\"How do flight bookings work on Cryptorefills?\",\"answer\":\"Cryptorefills uses a fully IATA and ARC accredited flight provider, Duffel to provide you with a seamless flight booking experience.  When you choose to book a flight through Cryptorefills, Duffel's API connects you to a wide range of airlines and flight options, allowing you to search, book, and manage your flights directly from our platform.\",\"link\":null},{\"subject\":\"Flights\",\"question\":\"Which cryptocurrencies can be used to pay for flights?\",\"answer\":\"You can pay for your booking with all the cryptocurrencies and wallets that we support. The only exception is BTC payments on the mainnet, due to the short expiration times associated with flight bookings. This ensures faster transaction processing and reduces the risk of price fluctuations affecting your booking.\",\"link\":null},{\"subject\":\"Flights\",\"question\":\"Can I make changes to my flight?\",\"answer\":\"In some cases yes, you can make changes to your flight bookings*. To do so, log into your Cryptorefills account or create one using the email address you provided during your booking. Navigate to your order history, and from there, you can initiate a chat with a Duffel support agent to request changes to your flight. *Please note that not all bookings can be changed, pay particular attention to the order change policy when selecting a flight if you think you'll need to make changes. Modifiying a booking may incur a fee, in accordance with the terms and conditions of the booking.\",\"link\":null},{\"subject\":\"Flights\",\"question\":\"Can I pay for flight changes with cryptocurrency?\",\"answer\":\"No, fees related to flight bookings (such as change fees or additional charges) must be paid in fiat currency. This policy ensures that the processing of changes is handled smoothly and efficiently.\",\"link\":null},{\"subject\":\"Flights\",\"question\":\"How secure are my transactions and personal information?\",\"answer\":\"Cryptorefills and Duffel prioritize the security of your transactions and personal information. Both platforms use advanced encryption and security measures to protect your data. Additionally, using cryptocurrencies for payment can offer an extra layer of security and privacy.\",\"link\":null},{\"subject\":\"Flights\",\"question\":\"Can I book international flights with crypto?\",\"answer\":\"Yes! You can book flights to and from any country where airlines are available on the Duffel platform. Cryptorefills supports global flight bookings with cryptocurrency, making it easy to pay for international travel with Bitcoin, USDT, USDC, and other cryptocurrencies.\",\"link\":null},{\"subject\":\"Flights\",\"question\":\"Do I need an account to book a flight?\",\"answer\":\"You don't need a Cryptorefills account to book a flight. However, creating an account allows you to track your orders and manage future bookings more easily. If you book without an account, we'll send your flight confirmation to the email address you provide during checkout.\",\"link\":null},{\"subject\":\"Flights\",\"question\":\"What happens if my flight is cancelled?\",\"answer\":\"If your flight is cancelled by the airline, you'll be entitled to a refund or rebooking according to the airline's policy and applicable regulations. Changes and refunds are managed through Duffel support. Please note that refunds for flight cancellations must be processed in fiat currency, in accordance with standard airline policies.\",\"link\":null}]}]}]}]]}]}]\n"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"54:T446,M202.91 15.1055C202.91 16.5147 204.319 16.9992 205.244 17.4616C206.653 17.924 208.063 18.8708 208.063 20.7645V72.2464H264.763V73.1933C264.763 73.6557 264.763 73.6557 264.763 74.6025C264.763 78.8523 266.173 81.6929 268.507 82.6397C268.507 82.6397 269.916 83.5865 271.788 83.5865C273.197 83.5865 274.606 83.1241 276.015 82.1773L276.962 81.7149L276.015 80.768C274.606 79.3588 273.681 75.5714 273.681 73.2153V72.7529H294.776V25.4987C294.776 25.4987 291.958 31.6422 281.652 39.195C281.652 39.195 282.115 41.0886 283.986 42.0355C286.805 43.4447 286.321 44.876 286.321 44.876V63.7689H273.197V62.822V61.8752C273.197 57.163 271.788 45.8229 259.148 45.8229H258.686C254.943 45.8229 251.199 45.8229 248.381 45.8229H247.434C239.947 45.8229 236.182 44.876 234.773 42.9823L234.31 42.0355L233.848 42.4979C232.438 43.4447 231.514 45.3384 231.514 47.2101C231.514 50.0506 233.385 53.816 236.204 53.816C238.076 53.816 240.894 53.816 243.713 53.816C248.403 53.816 253.555 53.816 253.555 53.816C263.861 53.816 264.323 58.5282 264.323 60.4219V62.778H216.496V0C216.496 0 210.881 7.55274 202.91 13.2338V13.6962V15.1055Z"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,"39:[\"$