iewBody\":\"Używam ich od ponad 2 lat i gorąco polecam. Bardzo szybkie i niezawodne.\"},{\"locale\":\"id\",\"reviewBody\":\"Saya sudah menggunakan mereka selama lebih dari 2 tahun dan sangat merekomendasikan. Sangat cepat dan dapat diandalkan.\"},{\"locale\":\"ja\",\"reviewBody\":\"2年以上使っており、とてもおすすめです。非常に迅速で信頼できます。\"},{\"locale\":\"ko\",\"reviewBody\":\"2년 넘게 사용해 왔으며 강력히 추천합니다. 매우 빠르고 신뢰할 수 있습니다.\"}],\"_fingerprint\":\"34804e228990b4b516a4b6c6dbfa65dbfccce48fdcbafe9c46cb8495424a4dd2\"},{\"name\":\"Sriwa Sofien\",\"reviewBody\":\"Merci beaucoup \\nService très rapide \\n5 Étoiles 🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟\",\"language\":\"fr\",\"reviewRating\":5,\"datePublished\":\"2026-06-03\",\"platform\":\"cryptorefills\",\"url\":null,\"image\":null,\"kinds\":[\"giftcards\"],\"isoCodes\":[\"GB\"],\"brands\":[\"Google Play\"],\"translations\":[{\"locale\":\"en\",\"reviewBody\":\"Thank you very much\\nVery fast service\\n5 Stars 🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟\"},{\"locale\":\"de\",\"reviewBody\":\"Vielen Dank\\nSehr schneller Service\\n5 Sterne 🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟\"},{\"locale\":\"es\",\"reviewBody\":\"Muchas gracias\\nServicio muy rápido\\n5 Estrellas 🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟\"},{\"locale\":\"it\",\"reviewBody\":\"Grazie mille\\nServizio molto veloce\\n5 Stelle 🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟\"},{\"locale\":\"tr\",\"reviewBody\":\"Çok teşekkürler\\nÇok hızlı servis\\n5 Yıldız 🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟\"},{\"locale\":\"tl\",\"reviewBody\":\"Maraming salamat\\nNapakabilis ng serbisyo\\n5 Bituin 🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟\"},{\"locale\":\"vi\",\"reviewBody\":\"Cảm ơn rất nhiều\\nDịch vụ rất nhanh\\n5 Sao 🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟\"},{\"locale\":\"zh\",\"reviewBody\":\"非常感谢\\n服务非常快速\\n5 星 🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟\"},{\"locale\":\"pt\",\"reviewBody\":\"Muito obrigado\\nServiço muito rápido\\n5 Estrelas 🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟\"},{\"locale\":\"hi\",\"reviewBody\":\"बहुत धन्यवाद\\nबहुत तेज़ सेवा\\n5 सितारे 🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟\"},{\"locale\":\"pl\",\"reviewBody\":\"Bardzo dziękuję\\nBardzo szybka obsługa\\n5 Gwiazdek 🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟\"},{\"locale\":\"id\",\"reviewBody\":\"Terima kasih banyak\\nLayanan sangat cepat\\n5 Bintang 🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟\"},{\"locale\":\"ja\",\"reviewBody\":\"どうもありがとうございます\\nとても迅速なサービス\\n星5つ 🌟🌟🌟🌟🌟\"},