ent method or try again later.\",\"it_looks_like_this_coupon_isnt_valid\":\" It looks like this coupon isn't valid for the email address you used. Please check the coupon's terms.\",\"maximum_amount_per_order_exceeded\":\"Maximum amount per order exceeded. Please remove some products from your cart.\",\"you_are_unable_to_create_orders_at_this_moment\":\"You are unable to create orders at this moment\",\"sorry_we_dont_currently_support_orders_from_your_country\":\"Sorry, we don't currently support orders from your country\",\"sorry_the_coupon_code\":\"Sorry, the coupon code {couponCode} has reached its maximum usage limit and can no longer be applied.\",\"please_go_back_and_remove_the_coupon_code_on_the_checkout_page\":\"Please go back and remove the coupon code on the checkout page\",\"it_looks_like_the_flight_you_selected_expire\":\"It looks like the flight you selected expired or is no longer available. Sorry about that. Please go back and search for flights\",\"please_only_pay_via_the_okx_chain\":\"Please only pay via the OKX chain. Sending funds through a different chain, such as Layer X, will result in the loss of your funds.\",\"do_not_use_layer_x\":\"Do NOT use Layer X / LayerX / OKX Layer X\",\"do_not_assume\":\"Do NOT assume “Layer X” is the same as OKX Chain\",\"we_re_sorry_but_you_ve_exceeded_the_maximum_number\":\"We're sorry, but you've exceeded the maximum number of products that can be delivered in a single day.\",\"refund_information\":\"Refund information\",\"enter_your_wallet_address_to_receive_your_refund\":\"Enter your wallet address to receive your refund\",\"reason\":\"Reason\",\"items\":\"Items\",\"wallet_address\":\"Wallet address\",\"enter_your_wallet_address\":\"Enter your wallet address\",\"wallet_address_is_required\":\"Wallet address is required\",\"failed_to_submit_wallet_address\":\"Failed to submit wallet address. Please try again.\",\"wallet_address_submitted_successfully\":\"Wallet address submitted successfully\",\"an_error_occurred_please_try_again\":\"An error occurred. Please try again.\",\"submitting\":\"Submitting...\",\"submit_wallet_address\":\"Submit wallet address\",\"refund_wallet\":\"Refund wallet\",\"refund_tx_hash\":\"Refund tx hash\",\"confirm_wallet_address\":\"I confirm this wallet address for refunds\",\"wallet_confirmation_disclaimer\":\"Once confirmed, this cannot be changed. Your refund will be sent to this address only.\",\"thank_you_your_wallet_address_has_been_received\":\"Thank you, your wallet address has been received. We'll process your refund within 48 hours.\",\"wallet_address_for_coin_on_network\":\"Wallet address for \u003ccoinIcon\u003e\u003c/coinIcon\u003e{coin} on the \u003cnetworkIcon\u003e\u003c/networkIcon\u003e{network} network\",\"installation_general\":\"General\",\"installation_click_to_install\":\"Click to install\",\"installation_tap_to_install\":\"Tap to install\",\"via\":\"via\",\"we_havent_detected_your_transaction_on_the_blockchain_within_the_payment_window\":\"We haven't detected your transaction on the blockchain within the payment window.\",\"we_didnt_receive_confirmation_of_your_payment_in_time\":\"We didn't receive confirmation of your payment in time.\",\"view_full_order_page\":\"View full order page\",\"order_created_with_date\":\"Order created {date}\",\"we_couldnt_find_this_order_please_check_the_order_id\":\"We couldn't find this order. Please check the order id.\"},\"Limits\":{\"purchase_amount\":\"Purchase amount\",\"day\":\"day\",\"month\":\"month\",\"remaining\":\"remaining\",\"certain_products_may_be_subject_to_unique_exceptional_thresholds\":\"Certain products may be subject to unique exceptional thresholds.\"},\"Account\":{\"title\":\"My Account - Cryptorefills\",\"cryptorefills_points\":\"Cryptorefills points\",\"earned\":\"Earned\",\"balance\":\"Balance\",\"your_cryptorefills_points_will_become_available_in_48_hours_after_your_purchase\":\"Your Cryptorefills points will become available in 48 hours after your purchase\",\"level_up_your_points_with_your_referral_link\":\"Level up your points with your referral link\",\"learn_more_about_the_referral_program\":\"Learn more about the referral program\",\"no_points_available\":\"No points available\",\"copy\":\"Copy\",\"copied\":\"Copied\",\"points_history\":\"Points history\",\"points\":\"points\",\"pending\":\"Pending\",\"to_activate_the_referral_campaign_you_need_to_complete_at_least_1_purchase\":\"To activate the referral camapign you need to complete at least 1 purchase\"},\"AccountOrders\":{\"title\":\"My Orders - Cryptorefills\",\"order_history\":\"Order history\",\"enter_your_order_id\":\"Enter your order id\",\"expired_orders\":\"Expired orders\",\"oops_something_went_wrong_while_retrieving_your_orders\":\"Oops! Something went wrong while retrieving your orders.\",\"sorry_we_couldnt_find_any_orders_associated_with_this_order_id\":\"Sorry, we couldn't find any orders associated with this order id.\",\"no_orders\":\"You don't have any orders yet.\",\"no_orders_browse_catalog\":\"Browse our catalog to get started.\",\"order_id\":\"Order id\",\"coin\":\"Coin\",\"network\":\"Network\",\"paid_with\":\"Paid with\",\"earned_cryptorefills_points\":\"Earned points\",\"valid_for_replace_category_only\":\"Valid for {replace} category only\",\"initial_amount_after_discount\":\"Amount after discount\",\"initial_amount\":\"Initial amount\",\"total_amount\":\"Total amount\",\"received_coin_amount\":\"Received coin amount\",\"missing_amount\":\"Missing amount\",\"no_products_available\":\"No products available\",\"invoices\":\"invoices\",\"download_invoice\":\"Download invoice\",\"download_proforma\":\"Download pro forma\",\"download_as_csv\":\"Download as CSV\",\"need_help_with_your_order_contact_us\":\"Need help with your order? Contact us!\",\"your_payment_for_the_order_has_not_been_received\":\" Your payment for the order has not been received. Please ensure completion of your order by sending the specified amount.\",\"complete_order\":\"Complete order\",\"waiting_for_confirmation_on_the_network\":\"Waiting for confirmation on the network.\",\"see_order_status\":\"View order status\",\"processing_your_order\":\"Processing your order\",\"your_payment_is_currently_being_processed_please_hold_on_a_moment\":\"Your payment is currently being processed. Please hold on a moment.\",\"sit_tight_we_re_working_on_processing_the_redemption_of_your_nft_gift_cards\":\"Sit tight! We're working on processing the redemption of your Programmable gift cards.\",\"we_have_not_received_any_payment_for_this_order\":\"We have not received any payment for this order.\",\"we_have_not_receive_the_complete_payment_for_this_order\":\"We have not received the full payment for this order.\",\"waiting_for_payment\":\"Waiting for payment\",\"waiting_for_delivery\":\"Waiting for delivery\",\"waiting_for_nft_giftcards\":\"Waiting for NFT gift cards\",\"waiting_for_rebuy\":\"Waiting for rebuy\",\"expired\":\"Expired\",\"payment_failed\":\"Payment failed\",\"waiting_for_manual_action\":\"Waiting for manual action\",\"waitingforpayment\":\"Waiting for payment\",\"done\":\"Completed\",\"refunded\":\"Refunded\",\"succeeded\":\"Succeeded\",\"paymentstarted\":\"Payment started\",\"waitingfordelivery\":\"Waiting for delivery\",\"waitingformanualaction\":\"Waiting for manual action\",\"paymentfailed\":\"Payment failed\",\"coupon_code\":\"Coupon code\",\"canceled\":\"Canceled\",\"wallet_address\":\"Wallet address\",\"store\":\"Store\",\"refund_waiting_for_refund_information\":\"Waiting for refund information\",\"refund_waiting_for_refund\":\"Waiting for refund approval\",\"refund_done\":\"Completed\",\"refund_cancelled\":\"Cancelled\",\"refund_no_reply\":\"No reply\",\"reason_failed_delivery\":\"Failed delivery\",\"refund_refund_failed\":\"Refund failed\",\"refund_processing\":\"Refund processing\",\"reason_your_payment_was_flagged_for_review\":\"Your payment was flagged for review.\",\"reason_your_order_has_expired\":\"Your order has expired.\",\"reason_one_or_more_products_could_not_be_delivered\":\"One or more products could not be delivered.\",\"reason_the_delivered_code_was_reported_as_not_working\":\"The delivered code was reported as not working.\"},\"TermsOfService\":{\"title\":\"Terms of service - Cryptorefills\",\"description\":\"Terms of service\",\"h1\":\"Terms of service\"},\"Contact\":{\"title\":\"Contact us - Cryptorefills\",\"description\":\"Get in touch with Cryptorefills Company's support team. We're here to assist you with any inquiries, feedback, or assistance you may need. Fill out the contact form or find our contact details here.\",\"get_in_touch\":\"Get in touch\",\"reason_of_contact\":\"Reason of contact\",\"whether_you_ve_got_a_question_about_your_order_or_a_product_we_re_here_to_help_you_out\":\"Whether you've got a question about an order, a product request, or a new feature we're here for you.\",\"you_can_talk_to_our_support_team_by_contact_form_email_or_use_our_social_media_channels\":\"You can talk to our support team by contact form, email, or use our social media channels.\",\"please_do_not_contact_us_with_multiple_requests_about_the_same_subject\":\"Please do not contact us with multiple requests about the same subject.\",\"we_will_respond_within_48_hours_filling_out_the_contact_form_or_emailing_multiple_times_will_result_in_slower_response_times\":\"We will respond within 48 hours. Filling out the contact form or emailing multiple times will result in slower response times.\",\"for_questions_regarding_your_order_please_fill_out_the_contact_form\":\"For questions regarding your order, please fill out the contact form.\",\"form_submission_error_instructions\":\"Oops, something didn't go as planned. Please email your question to info@cryptorefills.com. Also, include information on how to replicate the issue with the form submission.\",\"please_note_that_our_support_team_is_available_on_working_days_from_monday_to_friday_between_9_am_to_6_pm_central_european_time\":\"Please note that our support team is available on working days from Monday to Friday between 9 am to 6 pm Central European Time.\",\"take_a_look_at_our\":\"Take a look at our\",\"faqs\":\"FAQs\",\"your_question_might_have_already_been_answered\":\"Your question might have already been answered.\",\"reach_out\":\"Reach out\",\"explore_collaboration_possibilities\":\"Explore collaboration possibilities\",\"partnerships\":\"Partnerships\",\"partnerships_inquiry_form_meta_title\":\"Partnerships inquiry form\",\"partnerships_inquiry_form_meta_description\":\"Leverage Cryptorefills advanced platform and vast crypto user network to reach millions of potential customers and boost product sales worldwide.\",\"partnerships_inquiry_form_title\":\"Partnerships inquiry form\",\"partnerships_inquiry_form_intro\":\"Thank you for your interest in partnering with us!\",\"partnerships_inquiry_form_body_1\":\"Leverage the Cryptorefills platform to offer your users to spend their crypto for everyday services. Easily integrate our catalog into your application and offer your users an alternative crypto off-ramp experience!\",\"partnerships_inquiry_form_body_2\":\"Please tell us more about your business by filling out the form and getting in touch with our team.\",\"partnerships_api_docs_note\":\"Take a look at the possibilities in our API guide.\",\"partnerships_api_docs_cta\":\"Open API developers guide\",\"suppliers\":\"Suppliers\",\"careers\":\"Careers\",\"pressandmedia\":\"Press \u0026 media\",\"company_name\":\"Company name\",\"company_website\":\"Company website\",\"type_of_gift_cards_offered\":\"Type of gift cards offered\",\"target_market\":\"Target market\",\"partnership_details\":\"Partnership details\",\"name\":\"Name\",\"thank_you_message\":\"For taking the time to fill out this form. Our team will review your submission and get back to you as soon as possible.\",\"gift_card_types_example\":\"e.g. Retail, mobile top up, travel, etc.\",\"target_market_example\":\"e.g. US, Europe, Asia, etc.\",\"company_overview_prompt\":\"Briefly describe your company and gift card offerings:\",\"unique_value_prompt\":\"What makes your gift cards/service unique?\",\"additional_info_prompt\":\"Is there any additional information you would like to share with us?\",\"event\":\"Event\",\"additional_details\":\"Additional details\",\"event_issue_prompt\":\"Briefly describe your issues regarding the event\",\"main_social_media_profile\":\"Main social media profile\",\"briefly_describe_your_companies\":\"Briefly describe your companies\",\"briefly_describe_your_business_inquiry\":\"Briefly describe your business inquiry\",\"social_media_profile_placeholder\":\"e.g. @facebook @instagram @x\",\"brand_product_request\":\"Brand / product request\",\"feature_request\":\"Feature request\",\"out_of_stock\":\"Out of stock\",\"refund_request\":\"Refund request / change order\",\"flight_or_stay_booking\":\"Flight or stay booking\",\"kyc_approval\":\"KYC approval\",\"paid_wrong_coin_or_network\":\"Paid with the wrong coin or network\",\"i_paid_wrong_coin_or_network\":\"I paid with the wrong coin or network\",\"please_provide_details\":\"Please provide details about your payment\",\"coin_symbol\":\"Coin symbol\",\"network\":\"Network\",\"tx_hash\":\"Tx hash\",\"what_is_a_tx_hash\":\"What is a tx hash?\",\"a_transaction_hash_tx_hash\":\"A transaction hash (tx hash) is a unique ID on the blockchain that lets you track and verify a specific payment from start to finish you can find it in your wallet after sending a transaction or on a blockchain explorer.\",\"what_to_do_if_you_sent_the_wrong_coin_or_used_the_wrong_blockchain_network\":\"What to do if you sent the wrong coin or used the wrong blockchain network. \u003clink\u003eHow to find your Transaction Hash?\u003c/link\u003e\",\"it_is_important_to_pay_with_the_same_coin\":\"It is important to pay with the same coin and network selected on the checkout page and showed on the payment page.\",\"if_you_mistakenly_paid_with_the_wrong_coin_or_network\":\"If you mistakenly paid with the wrong coin or network, we may be able to manually recover your payment and deliver your order.\",\"make_sure_you_copy_the_transaction\":\"Make sure you copy the transaction hash that can be found on a blockchain explorer\",\"wallet_address_in_case_of_a_refund\":\"Your {coin} {network} wallet address in case of a refund\",\"order_not_delivered\":\"Order not delivered\",\"issue_redeeming_gift_card\":\"Issue redeeming gift card\",\"missing_barcode\":\"Missing barcode\",\"other_reason\":\"Other reason\",\"order_id\":\"Order id\",\"optional\":\"Optional\",\"email\":\"Email\",\"exampleemailcom\":\"example@email.com\",\"message\":\"Message\",\"please_enter_a_valid_order_id\":\"Please enter a valid order id\",\"message_is_too_short\":\"Message is too short\",\"invalid_recaptcha\":\"Invalid reCaptcha\",\"submitting_multiple_tickets\":\"Submitting multiple tickets for the same issue can delay response times. Please wait at least 15 minutes before creating a new ticket and avoid multiple submissions on the same topic. Thank you for your understanding.\",\"submit\":\"Submit\",\"select_topic\":\"Select a topic\",\"thank_you\":\"Thank you\",\"is_the_order_still_pending_in_the_world_app\":\"Is the order still pending in the World app?\",\"please_note_that_you_can_also_view_your_order_on_cryptorefills\":\"Please note that you can also view your order on Cryptorefills\",\"see_all_your_orders_by_creating_a_cryptorefills\":\"See all your orders by creating a Cryptorefills account with the same email address used to place your order\",\"we_have_received_your_message\":\"We've received your message and will get back to you within 48 hours.\",\"the_product_from_your_order\":\" The product from your order doesn't match the country you are in. Please note that the product page clearly states that the product will only work in the country mentioned on the product page.\",\"please_be_advised_that\":\"Please be advised that, at this moment, we cannot process any refunds or changes regarding a country mismatch with your order.\",\"please_note_that_your_order_has_not_been_delivered_yet_as_we_have_not_detected_any_payment_from_you\":\"Please note that your order has not been delivered yet, as we have not detected any payment from you.\",\"complete_your_order_on_the_order_payment_page\":\"Complete your order on the order payment page\",\"unfortunately_we_were_unable_to_deliver_your_order_user_wallet\":\"Unfortunately, we were unable to deliver your order. The full amount has already been refunded in {coin} on {network}.\",\"unfortunately_we_were_unable_to_deliver_your_order\":\"Unfortunately, we were unable to deliver your order. The full amount has already been refunded.\",\"refund_wallet_address\":\"Refund wallet address\",\"view_the_transaction_on_the_blockchain_explorer\":\"View the transaction on the blockchain explorer\",\"your_order_has_been_successfully_delivered\":\"Your order has been successfully delivered\",\"if_you_dont_see_the_top_up_yet_short\":\"If you don’t see the top-up reflected on your number yet, we recommend first contacting your mobile operator directly.\",\"operator_reference\":\"Operator reference\",\"if_you_dont_see_the_top_up_yet\":\"If you don’t see the top-up yet, we recommend first checking directly with your mobile operator and sharing the operator reference with them, they can usually confirm the status quickly.\",\"when_speaking_with_your_operator_please_provide_the_following_reference_details\":\"When speaking with your operator, please provide the following reference details:\",\"if_the_top_up_is_still_not_visible_after_that\":\"If the top-up is still not visible after contacting your operator, please reach out to us again. We’ll be happy to assist you further.\",\"please_note_that_your_order_hasnt_been_delivered_yet_as_the_payment_hasnt_been_confirmed_on_the_network_yet\":\"Please note that your order hasn't been delivered yet, as the payment hasn't been confirmed on the network yet.\",\"see_the_latest_status_of_your_order_on_the_payment_page\":\"See the latest status of your order on the payment page\",\"please_note_that_your_order_hasnt_been_delivered_yet_as_we_havent_detected_any_payment_from_you\":\"Please note that your order hasn't been delivered yet, as we haven't detected any payment from you.\",\"please_note_that_it_is_not_possible_to_get_a_refund_or_change_your_order_after_we_have_delivered_your_order_succesfully\":\"For gift card products, please note that it is not possible to get a refund or change your order after we have delivered your order successfully.\",\"we_are_unable_to_change_the_redemption_country_of_your_product\":\"We are unable to change the redemption country of your product.\",\"in_accordance_with_the_companys_kyc_and_aml_tf\":\"In accordance with the company's KYC and AML/TF policies we request certain information from the user and limit the amounts that users can spend on products within specific time frames based on user tiers as defined in our terms and conditions\",\"log_in_to_your_account_to_view_your\":\"Log in to your account to view your spending limits\",\"on_your_account_page\":\"on your account page\",\"verify_your_account_by_visiting_the\":\"Verify your account by visiting your\",\"settings_page_under_your_account\":\"account page\",\"please_note_that_kyc_verification_can_take_up_to_48_hours\":\"Please note that KYC verification can take up to 48 hours. If you experience any issues, please submit this form.\",\"google_play_is_strict_when_it_comes_to_redemption\":\"Google Play is strict when it comes to redemption. To avoid issues with your Google Play gift card, only redeem and use Google Play gift cards that are valid in both your country and the country of your Google account.\",\"read_google_play_redemption_error_contact_google_support_journey\":\"Read Google Play redemption error, contact Google support journey\",\"upload_image\":\"Upload image\",\"please_provide_a_screenshot_of_the_issue_including_the_url_if_possible\":\"Please provide a screenshot of the issue, including the URL, if possible.\",\"drop_here\":\"Drop the image here...\",\"drag_or_click\":\"Drag 'n' drop some image here, or click to select image\",\"attached_files\":\"Attached files\",\"we_do_our_best_to_restock_our_product_as_soon_as_possible\":\"We do our best to restock our product as soon as possible. Unfortunately, no precise restock date is available. We recommend checking our website regularly\",\"upload_failed_fileName_exceeds_the_10_mb_size_limit\":\"Upload failed {fileName} exceeds the 10 MB size limit.\",\"maximum_upload_limit_files\":\"Please note that you can upload up to 5 files\",\"file_type_not_supported\":\"Unsupported file type\",\"we_always_strive_to_add_a_barcode_to_your_product_if_applicable\":\"We always strive to add a barcode to your product if applicable. In case something goes wrong during this process, a barcode can usually be generated using the serial code and a barcode generator with Code-128.\",\"generate_your_barcode_with_a_website_like\":\"Generate your barcode with a website like\",\"select_code_128_enter_the_serial_code_and_click\":\"Select Code-128, enter the serial code, and click 'Generate'. (Do not include the pins if any are present.)\",\"if_you_re_experiencing_issues_with_brand_redeem_codes\":\"If you're experiencing issues with {brand} redeem codes, please reach out to {brand2} official support team, as  the problem is likely related to your account.\",\"contact_brand_official_support\":\"Contact {brand} official support\",\"need_help_choose_the_right_option_below_to_get_in_touch\":\"Need help? Choose the right option below to get in touch\",\"for_any_questions_about_your_account_please_reach_out_to_world_support\":\"For any questions about your account, please reach out to World support.\",\"contact_world_support\":\"Contact World support\",\"if_you_have_questions_about_your_gift_card_or_mobile_top_up_orde\":\"If you have questions about your gift card or mobile top-up order, contact Cryptorefills support. We're here to help with your order.\",\"contact_cryptorefills\":\"Contact Cryptorefills\",\"by_submitting_this_form_you_will_contact_cryptorefills_support_for_gift_cards_and_mobile_topups\":\"By submitting this form, you will contact Cryptorefills support for gift cards and mobile top-ups.\",\"for_questions_regarding_your_world_account\":\"For questions regarding your World account\",\"visit_world_support_page\":\"visit World support page\",\"changes_and_any_enquiries_regarding_your_flight_or_stay\":\"Changes and any enquiries regarding your flight or stay can be made on \u003clink\u003e your order history page\u003c/link\u003e.\",\"clear_order_id\":\"Clear order id\"},\"NotFound\":{\"sorry_we_cant_find_the_page_you_are_looking_for\":\"Sorry, we can't find the page you are looking for.\",\"home\":\"Home\",\"gift_cards\":\"Gift cards\",\"mobile_top_ups\":\"Mobile top ups\",\"helpful_links\":\"Helpful links\"},\"Investors\":{\"title\":\"Investors - Cryptorefills\",\"description\":\"Investors\"},\"Careers\":{\"title\":\"Cryptorefills careers\",\"description\":\"Participate in a global team of innovators, visionaries, and creators, United by the power of crypto and Web3.\"},\"PressMedia\":{\"title\":\"Press \u0026 media - Cryptorefills\",\"description\":\"Participate in a global team of innovators, visionaries, and creators, United by the power of crypto and Web3.\",\"press_and_media\":\"Press \u0026 media\",\"unveiling_the_future_stay_informed\":\"Unveiling the future: stay informed\",\"view_brand_identity\":\"Explore our brand identity\",\"for_information_and_press_enquiries\":\"For information and press enquiries\",\"see_all_news\":\"See all news\",\"about\":\"About\"},\"ConsumerAndDigitalBrands\":{\"title\":\"Consumer \u0026 digital brands - Cryptorefills\",\"description\":\"Leverage Cryptorefills platform and technology to sell your products to millions of crypto users all over the world.\"},\"WalletsAndExchanges\":{\"title\":\"Wallets \u0026 exchanges - Cryptorefills\",\"description\":\"Leverage Cryptorefills platform to offer your users to spend their crypto for everyday services.\"},\"ForBrands\":{\"title\":\"For brands - Cryptorefills\",\"description\":\"Reach 560M+ crypto owners globally. Distribute your gift cards, digital products and services to hundreds of thousands of active crypto buyers through Cryptorefills platform and exchange partners.\",\"hero_heading\":\"Your brand, where crypto gets spent\",\"hero_subheading\":\"One integration. Direct access to hundreds of thousands of active buyers across 180+ countries, including markets where card payments don't reach.\",\"hero_cta_partnerships\":\"Talk to partnerships\",\"hero_cta_how_it_works\":\"See how it works\",\"hero_settlement_heading\":\"Settle on your terms. In hours, not weeks.\",\"hero_settlement_tab_fiat\":\"Fiat\",\"hero_settlement_tab_stablecoin\":\"Stablecoin\",\"hero_settlement_tab_btc\":\"BTC\",\"hero_settlement_time_same_day\":\"Same-day\",\"hero_settlement_time_real_time\":\"Real-time\",\"hero_settlement_time_daily\":\"Daily\",\"hero_settlement_time_instant\":\"Instant\",\"hero_settlement_time_t1\":\"T+1\",\"hero_coin_carousel_heading\":\"*Or in minutes\",\"sales_pitch_heading\":\"Crypto buyers are already spending\",\"sales_pitch_subheading\":\"Make sure they're spending on you\",\"sales_pitch_badge_numbers\":\"Numbers\",\"sales_pitch_stat_operating_since\":\"Operating since\",\"sales_pitch_stat_countries\":\"Countries\",\"sales_pitch_stat_gift_card_brands\":\"Gift card brands\",\"sales_pitch_stat_emerging_markets\":\"Orders to emerging markets\",\"sales_pitch_stat_delivered\":\"Delivered \u003c 10s\",\"sales_pitch_stat_chargebacks\":\"Zero chargebacks\",\"sales_pitch_stat_chargebacks_display\":\"Zero\",\"sales_pitch_badge_fees\":\"Fees\",\"sales_pitch_fees_heading\":\"No listing fees.\",\"sales_pitch_fees_body\":\"You only pay when you earn. Revenue share on redemption only, no upfront cost, no platform minimums.\",\"sales_pitch_fees_row_listing\":\"Listing fee\",\"sales_pitch_fees_row_setup\":\"Setup cost\",\"sales_pitch_fees_row_revenue\":\"Revenue share\",\"sales_pitch_fees_row_revenue_value\":\"On redemption\",\"sales_pitch_badge_control\":\"Control\",\"sales_pitch_control_heading\":\"Every aspect of your listing.\",\"sales_pitch_control_body\":\"A complete self-service portal. Set markets, pricing, timing, brand assets and inventory thresholds. Enable or disable SKUs in seconds.\",\"sales_pitch_control_tag_markets\":\"Markets\",\"sales_pitch_control_tag_pricing\":\"Pricing\",\"sales_pitch_control_tag_timing\":\"Timing\",\"sales_pitch_control_tag_assets\":\"Assets\",\"sales_pitch_control_tag_inventory\":\"Inventory\",\"sales_pitch_control_tag_kill_switch\":\"Kill switch\",\"purchase_flow_heading\":\"How buyers pay with crypto\",\"purchase_flow_subheading\":\"Three steps to your code\",\"purchase_flow_step_1_title\":\"Browse, select and configure\",\"purchase_flow_step_1_description\":\"Search 6,600+ brands across 180+ countries. Pick your product, choose the denomination and quantity, then select which crypto you want to pay with.\",\"purchase_flow_step_2_title\":\"Review and create your order\",\"purchase_flow_step_2_description\":\"Check your order details, pick your preferred blockchain network and coin, then click 'Continue to payment'.\",\"purchase_flow_step_3_title\":\"Pay and get your code instantly\",\"purchase_flow_step_3_description\":\"Scan the QR code or copy the payment address. Send from your wallet and receive your gift card code instantly.\",\"exchanges_heading\":\"One integration\",\"exchanges_subheading\":\"Reach into the exchanges and wallets where hundreds of millions of crypto users already are\",\"integration_heading\":\"Intro call to live\",\"integration_subheading\":\"Under a week, start to finish\",\"integration_step_1_title\":\"Intro call\",\"integration_step_1_description\":\"30 min to align on catalogue, pricing, and integration path.\",\"integration_step_2_title\":\"Contract and SKU upload\",\"integration_step_2_description\":\"Sign the agreement, share your catalogue. We handle the rest.\",\"integration_step_3_title\":\"Test in staging\",\"integration_step_3_description\":\"Validate end-to-end before anything goes live.\",\"integration_step_4_title\":\"Live in production\",\"integration_step_4_description\":\"Your products live across Cryptorefills and all partners.\",\"integration_card_api_badge\":\"Integration\",\"integration_card_api_heading\":\"API or managed stock\",\"integration_card_api_body\":\"Full REST API for large-scale partners. No-API managed stock model for brands without engineering infrastructure. Both paths reach the same distribution network.\",\"integration_card_api_option_rest_label\":\"REST API\",\"integration_card_api_option_rest_sub\":\"For engineering teams\",\"integration_card_api_option_managed_label\":\"Managed stock\",\"integration_card_api_option_managed_sub\":\"No engineering needed\",\"integration_card_api_cta\":\"Talk to partnerships\",\"integration_card_docs_badge\":\"API docs\",\"integration_card_docs_heading\":\"Developer-first documentation\",\"integration_card_docs_body\":\"Full API reference, authentication guide, webhook documentation, and live sandbox. Get from zero to first order in hours, not weeks.\",\"integration_card_ai_badge\":\"AI agents\",\"integration_card_ai_badge_new\":\"New\",\"integration_card_ai_heading\":\"Discoverable by every AI agent\",\"integration_card_ai_body\":\"Cryptorefills exposes MCP APIs and supports x402 micropayment headers. Your products become natively accessible to autonomous AI agents without human checkout steps.\",\"integration_card_ai_chat_request\":\"Find me a $25 Amazon gift card.\",\"integration_card_ai_chat_paying\":\"Found it. Paying via x402...\",\"integration_card_ai_chat_delivered\":\"Code delivered. No human needed.\",\"integration_card_ai_cta\":\"Explore AI agents\",\"integration_footer_text\":\"Driving consumer adoption of crypto in ecommerce since 2018\",\"integration_footer_cta\":\"Our story\",\"faq_heading\":\"Common questions from brands\",\"faq_q1\":\"What types of products can I sell on Cryptorefills?\",\"faq_a1\":\"Cryptorefills supports digital products including gift cards, gaming credits, eSIM, mobile top up, travel bookings and subscription services. If you sell a digital or redeemable product, there is likely a place for it on our platform.\",\"faq_q2\":\"Do I need to integrate via API to list my products?\",\"faq_a2\":\"No. We offer both API-based integrations for large-scale partners and a managed stock model for mid-size brands that don't have API infrastructure. Our team handles the operational setup.\",\"faq_q3\":\"How does Cryptorefills handle settlement and chargebacks?\",\"faq_a3\":\"You see live sales in your portal as they happen, and invoice us on your own schedule. Most brands run monthly. We pay the invoice same-day in EUR, T+1 in USD, GBP, CHF or MXN, faster on stablecoins or BTC. Crypto rails don't reverse, so there are no chargebacks, and consumer-side disputes are ours to handle.\",\"faq_q4\":\"How does Cryptorefills distribute products beyond its own website?\",\"faq_a4\":\"Cryptorefills has distribution partnerships with major crypto exchanges and wallets including KuCoin, Bitget, Kraken, World and others. Products listed with us are surfaced across these platforms, extending reach beyond our direct user base, including in regions where card-based distribution is thin.\",\"faq_q5\":\"What is B2A and how does it apply to my brand?\",\"faq_a5\":\"B2A (Business to Agent) is a new commercial channel where AI agents autonomously discover and purchase products on behalf of users. Cryptorefills supports MCP APIs and the x402 payment protocol, making listed products natively accessible to AI shopping agents, a rapidly growing segment.\",\"faq_q6\":\"What currencies does Cryptorefills accept?\",\"faq_a6\":\"We accept all major stablecoins including USDT and USDC, Bitcoin (including via Lightning Network for instant low-fee payments) and all other leading crypto. We are also the first ecommerce platform to accept stablecoin payments via alternative networks including Avalanche, Solana and Polygon.\"},\"SpendCrypto\":{\"title\":\"Spend Crypto online: gift cards, mobile top ups, eSIMs, flights, hotels | Cryptorefills\",\"description\":\"Spend crypto directly from your wallet - no KYC required. Buy gift cards, flights, hotel stays, mobiel top ups and eSIMs with Bitcoin, USDT, USDC, ETH and 100+ more coins at 6,600+ brands worldwide.\",\"schema_breadcrumb_home\":\"Home\",\"schema_breadcrumb_spend_crypto\":\"Spend Crypto\",\"schema_howto_name\":\"How to Spend Crypto on Cryptorefills\",\"schema_howto_description\":\"Step-by-step guide to spending cryptocurrency at 6,600+ brands without KYC.\",\"schema_howto_step_1_name\":\"Choose a product\",\"schema_howto_step_1_text\":\"Browse gift cards, flights, hotel stays, or eSIMs at Cryptorefills.\",\"schema_howto_step_2_name\":\"Select your cryptocurrency\",\"schema_howto_step_2_text\":\"Choose from Bitcoin, USDT, USDC, ETH, DOGE, LTC and 100+ supported coins.\",\"schema_howto_step_3_name\":\"Pay from your wallet\",\"schema_howto_step_3_text\":\"Send crypto directly from your wallet or exchange with no KYC required.\",\"schema_howto_step_4_name\":\"Receive your purchase\",\"schema_howto_step_4_text\":\"Your gift card code, eSIM, or booking confirmation is delivered instantly.\",\"schema_video_name\":\"How to Spend Crypto on Cryptorefills\",\"schema_video_description\":\"Watch how easy it is to buy gift cards, flights, and more using Bitcoin or stablecoins on Cryptorefills.\",\"spend_crypto\":\"Spend Crypto online: Buy gift cards, flights, hotels and more\",\"spend_crypto_from_any_wallet_or_exchange_at_over_6600_brands\":\"Spend Crypto from any wallet or exchange at over 6600 brands that accept cryptocurrency payments. Pay with Bitcoin (BTC), Ethereum (ETH), Tether (USDT), USDC, Dogecoin (DOGE), or Litecoin (LTC) on networks such as Avalanche, Polygon, Solana, Tron, Base, Binance Chain, World Chain, Ton, and Arbitrum.\",\"buy_products_with_crypto_like_cash_discover_the_difference\":\"Buy products with Crypto like cash — discover the differences between various blockchain networks and learn which products you can purchase with cryptocurrency.\",\"spend_crypto_direct_from_your_wallet_or_exchange_buy_gift_ca\":\"Spend Crypto direct from your wallet or exchange buy gift cards, mobile topups, eSIMs, flights or book your hotel.\",\"44_on_trustpilot_reviews\":\"{rating} on Trustpilot reviews\",\"view_our_brands\":\"View our brands\",\"understanding_coins_tokens_networks\":\"Understanding Coins Tokens \u0026 Networks\",\"tokens\":\"Tokens\",\"a_token_like_usdc_is_a_digital_asset_that_represents_value_a\":\"A token like USDC is a digital asset that represents value and can be transferred on different blockchain networks.\",\"it_runs_on_a_smart_contract_which_is_a_self_executing_progra\":\"It runs on a smart contract, which is a self-executing program on the blockchain that keeps it secure, transparent, and follows set rules.\",\"coins\":\"Coins\",\"a_coin_like_eth_is_a_digital_asset_that_operates_on_its_own_\":\"A coin like ETH is a digital asset that operates on its own native blockchain and is used as a medium of exchange or store of value.\",\"it_is_secured_by_the_blockchains_consensus_mechanism_such_a\":\"It is secured by the blockchain's consensus mechanism, such as Proof of Work or Proof of Stake, ensuring transparency and decentralized control.\",\"networks_blockchains\":\"Networks (blockchains)\",\"a_network_like_arbitrum_is_a_blockchain_layer_that_facilitat\":\"A network like Arbitrum is a blockchain layer that facilitates transactions and smart contracts, improving speed and reducing costs.\",\"blockchains_are_built_in_layers_to_improve_scalability_effic\":\"Blockchains are built in layers to improve scalability, efficiency, and cost-effectiveness.\",\"layer_1_blockchains\":\"Layer 1 blockchains\",\"like_ethereum_or_bitcoin_is_the_base_network_that_handles_tr\":\"Like Ethereum or Bitcoin is the base network that handles transactions and security directly.\",\"layer_2_blockchains\":\"Layer 2 blockchains\",\"like_arbitrum_or_lightning_network_is_built_on_top_of_layer\":\"Like Arbitrum or Lightning Network is built on top of Layer 1 to process transactions faster and cheaper while still relying on its security.\",\"token\":\"Token\",\"what_is_a_stablecoin\":\"What is a stablecoin?\",\"stablecoins_are_a_type_of_cryptocurrency_whose_value_is_pegg\":\"Stablecoins are a type of cryptocurrency whose value is pegged to another asset, such as a fiat currency or gold, to maintain a stable price.\",\"cryptorefills_supports_the_most_popular_stablecoins_as_usdt_\":\"Cryptorefills supports the most popular stablecoins as USDT, USDC, DAI, EUROC, PYUSD, FDUSD, USDC.e and USDT.e.\",\"difference_in_popular_stablecoins\":\"Difference in popular stablecoins\",\"stablecoins_are_pegged_to_fiat_currencies_but_differ_in_issu\":\"Stablecoins are pegged to fiat currencies, but differ in issuers, collateral backing (fiat, crypto, or algorithmic), and blockchain networks, or wrapped versions on non-native blockchains.\",\"stablecoins_supported_by_cryptorefills\":\"Stablecoins supported by Cryptorefills\",\"usdt_tether_is_a_fiat_backed_stablecoin_pegged_to_the_us_dol\":\"USDT (Tether) is a fiat-backed stablecoin pegged to the US dollar, issued by Tether Limited and primarily backed by reserves like cash and equivalents.\",\"usdte_is_a_wrapped_version_of_usdt_issued_on_a_non_native_bl\":\"USDT.e is a wrapped version of USDT issued on a non-native blockchain, typically representing USDT bridged from its original network (e.g., Ethereum) to another chain like Avalanche or Arbitrum, and is not issued directly by Tether but by third-party bridge operators.\",\"dai_is_a_decentralized_crypto_collateralized_stablecoin_pegg\":\"DAI is a decentralized, crypto-collateralized stablecoin pegged to the US dollar, issued by MakerDAO and backed by overcollateralized assets like ETH, USDC, and other cryptocurrencies through smart contracts.\",\"usdc_usd_coin_is_a_fiat_backed_stablecoin_pegged_to_the_us_d\":\"USDC (USD Coin) is a fiat-backed stablecoin pegged to the US dollar, issued by Circle and primarily backed by reserves like cash and short-term US government bonds.\",\"usdce_is_a_wrapped_version_of_usdc_issued_on_a_non_native_bl\":\"USDC.e is a wrapped version of USDC issued on a non-native blockchain, typically representing USDC bridged from its original network (e.g., Ethereum) to another chain like Avalanche or Arbitrum, and is not issued directly by Circle but by third-party bridge operators.\",\"euroc_euro_coin_is_a_fiat_backed_stablecoin_pegged_to_the_eu\":\"EUROC (Euro Coin) is a fiat-backed stablecoin pegged to the euro, issued by Circle and primarily backed by reserves like cash and short-term European government bonds.\",\"pyusd_paypal_usd_is_a_fiat_backed_stablecoin_pegged_to_the_u\":\"PYUSD (PayPal USD) is a fiat-backed stablecoin pegged to the US dollar, issued by PayPal and primarily backed by reserves like cash and short-term US government bonds.\",\"fdusd_first_digital_usd_is_a_fiat_backed_stablecoin_pegged_t\":\"FDUSD (First Digital USD) is a fiat-backed stablecoin pegged to the US dollar, issued by First Digital Labs and primarily backed by reserves like cash and cash-equivalent assets.\",\"usde_is_a_crypto_backed_stablecoin\":\"USDE (Ethena USD) is a crypto-backed stablecoin pegged to the US dollar, issued by Ethena Labs. It maintains its peg through a delta-neutral hedging mechanism using collateral like ETH.\",\"usds_is_a_fiat_and_crypto_backed_stablecoin\":\"USDS (Sky USD) is a stablecoin pegged to the US dollar, issued by Sky (formerly MakerDAO). It is the successor to DAI and is backed by a mix of crypto and real-world assets.\",\"native_digital_currencies_fueling_the_blockchain_ecosystem\":\"Native digital currencies fueling the blockchain ecosystem\",\"coin\":\"Coin\",\"what_is_a_coin\":\"What is a Coin?\",\"native_digital_currencies\":\"Native digital currencies\",\"a_coin_like_bitcoin_btc_litecoin_ltc_and_dogecoin_doge_is_a_\":\"A coin, like Bitcoin (BTC), Litecoin (LTC) and Dogecoin (DOGE), is a digital asset that runs on its own blockchain and is primarily used for transactions, payments, or as a store of value. Unlike tokens, coins are native to their respective networks and are secured by consensus mechanisms like Proof of Work or Proof of Stake.\",\"fueling_the_blockchain_ecosystem\":\"Fueling the blockchain ecosystem\",\"a_coin_like_ethereum_eth_not_only_serves_as_a_currency_but_a\":\"A coin like Ethereum (ETH) not only serves as a currency but also plays a key role in powering its blockchain. On networks like Ethereum, ETH is required to pay for gas fees, which are transaction costs needed to execute smart contracts, including stablecoin transfers and other decentralized applications.\",\"cryptorefills_accepted_coins\":\"Cryptorefills accepted Coins\",\"at_cryptorefills_we_accept_bitcoin_btc_dogecoin_doge_and_lit\":\"At Cryptorefills, we accept Bitcoin (BTC), Dogecoin (DOGE), and Litecoin (LTC) for payments. However, when it comes to fueling blockchain transactions, we only support Ethereum (ETH), Solana (SOL), TON, and Worldcoin (WLD).\",\"not_accepted_coins\":\"Not accepted Coins\",\"we_do_not_accept_coins_like_avalanche_avax_tron_trx_or_solan\":\"We do not accept coins like Avalanche (AVAX) or Tron (TRX), even though these are required to cover gas fees when transferring stablecoins on their respective blockchains from your wallet or exchange.\",\"network_blockchain\":\"Network (blockchain)\",\"what_is_a_network_blockchain\":\"What is a Network (Blockchain)?\",\"blockchain_evolution_of_smart_contracts\":\"Blockchain evolution of Smart Contracts\",\"blockchains_like_bitcoin_are_designed_for_secure_transaction\":\"Blockchains like Bitcoin are designed for secure transactions, while networks like Ethereum enable smart contract deployment, allowing decentralized applications (dApps) and complex financial operations.\",\"evm_blockchains\":\"EVM blockchains\",\"ethereum_virtual_machine_evm_blockchains_including_ethereum_\":\"Ethereum Virtual Machine (EVM) blockchains, including Ethereum, Arbitrum, Avalanche, and others, share compatibility with Ethereum's smart contract ecosystem, enabling seamless deployment of decentralized applications across multiple chains.\",\"how_blockchains_validate_transactions\":\"How blockchains validate transactions?\",\"proof_of_work\":\"Proof of Work\",\"used_by_bitcoin_and_ethereum_before_its_upgrade_relying_on_m\":\"Used by Bitcoin and Ethereum (before its upgrade), relying on miners solving cryptographic puzzles to secure the network.\",\"proof_of_stake\":\"Proof of Stake\",\"used_by_ethereum_post_merge_relying_on_validators_staking_as\":\"Used by Ethereum post-Merge, relying on validators staking assets to confirm transactions.\",\"proof_of_history\":\"Proof of History\",\"used_by_solana_creating_a_cryptographic_timestamp_to_optimiz\":\"Used by Solana, creating a cryptographic timestamp to optimize validation speed.\",\"blockchain_performance_speed_and_transaction_costs\":\"Blockchain performance, speed and transaction costs\",\"ethereum_prioritizes_security_and_decentralization_but_has_h\":\"Ethereum prioritizes security and decentralization but has higher costs. Layer 2 Networks like Arbitrum improve scalability. Solana and Avalanche offer high-speed transactions with lower fees, while Tron remains a cost-effective option for payments.\",\"network_blockchain_solutions_supported_by_cryptorefills\":\"Network (Blockchain) solutions supported by Cryptorefills\",\"explore\":\"Explore\",\"ready_to_spend_crypto\":\"Ready to spend crypto?\",\"a_decentralized_blockchain_enabling_smart_contracts__powerin\":\"A decentralized blockchain enabling smart contracts, powering dApps, and secured by Proof of Stake. Ethereum prioritizes security and decentralization but has relative high transaction costs.\",\"a_popular_layer2_sidechain_solution_for_ethereum_that_provi\":\"A popular Layer-2/sidechain solution for Ethereum that provides faster and cheaper transactions. Polygon uses sidechains to process off-chain transactions before finalizing on Ethereum for security.\",\"an_ethereum_layer2_solution_that_employs_optimistic_rollups\":\"An Ethereum Layer-2 solution that employs optimistic rollups. It offers low-cost, high-throughput transactions while inheriting the security of Ethereum.\",\"a_highly_scalable_low_latency_blockchain_platform_that_supp\":\"A highly scalable, low-latency blockchain platform that supports smart contracts. Avalanche achieves sub-second finality and features customizable subnets for specialized use cases.\",\"an_ethereum_layer2_protocol_leveraging_optimistic_rollups_t\":\"An Ethereum Layer-2 protocol leveraging optimistic rollups to reduce transaction costs and increase throughput, all while maintaining the security of the Ethereum mainnet.\",\"a_blockchain_developed_by_binance_with_low_transaction_fees\":\"A blockchain developed by Binance with low transaction fees, EVM compatibility, and high throughput. It supports a vast ecosystem of decentralized applications and tokens.\",\"okx_chain_okc_is_an_evm_compatible_blockchain_developed_by\":\"OKX Chain (OKC) is an EVM-compatible blockchain developed by OKX, offering low fees, high performance, and cross-chain interoperability within the OKX ecosystem.\",\"a_coinbase_incubated_ethereum_layer2_network_built_using_op\":\"A Coinbase-incubated Ethereum Layer-2 network built using Optimism's technology. Base aims to offer secure, low-cost, and developer-friendly solutions for on-chain applications.\",\"a_high_performance_blockchain_designed_for_fast_and_low_cost\":\"A high-performance blockchain designed for fast and low-cost transactions. Tron is a Layer-1 network with high throughput and low fees, making it ideal for dApps, stablecoins, and DeFi.\",\"a_high_performance_layer1_blockchain_designed_for_ultra_fas\":\"A high-performance Layer-1 blockchain designed for ultra-fast and low-cost transactions. Solana uses a unique Proof-of-History (PoH) mechanism combined with Proof-of-Stake (PoS) to achieve high scalability, processing thousands of transactions per second. \",\"sonic_is_a_fast_and_scalable_layer_1\":\"Sonic is a fast and scalable Layer-1 blockchain that works with Ethereum. It uses a Proof-of-Stake system to make transactions quick and finish in under a second, great for decentralized apps.\",\"plasma_is_a_fast_and_scalable_layer_1\":\"Plasma is a fast and scalable Layer-1 blockchain built for quick, low-cost transactions and smooth decentralized app performance, and is developed with backing from Tether for efficient USDT transfers.\",\"ton_is_a_high_performance_layer_1\":\"TON (The Open Network) is a high-performance Layer-1 blockchain built for speed, low fees, and scalability. Using dynamic sharding and Proof-of-Stake, it supports fast, low-cost transactions and is deeply integrated with the Telegram ecosystem. Its native coin, formerly Toncoin, is now called GRAM.\",\"gram_is_the_native_coin_of_the_ton_blockchain\":\"GRAM is the native coin of TON (The Open Network), powering fees, staking, and transactions across the network. Rebranded from Toncoin in a 1:1 switch in June 2026, it offers the same fast, low-cost payments as TON, and Cryptorefills accepts it directly from your wallet.\",\"sui_is_a_high_performance_layer_1_blockchain\":\"Sui is a high-performance Layer-1 blockchain built for fast, low-cost transactions and scalable dApps. It uses a unique object-centric model and delegated Proof-of-Stake consensus to achieve parallel execution and near-instant finality.\"},\"HowItWorks\":{\"title\":\"How to buy gift cards with Bitcoin: A step-by-step guide\",\"description\":\"Discover the simple steps to buy gift cards with Bitcoin, Crypto and Binance. Learn how to use Bitcoin to purchase gift cards and enjoy the convenience and flexibility it offers.\",\"step_by_step_guide_how_to_buy_a_gift_card_with_bitcoin_and_crypto\":\"Step-by-step guide: how to buy gift cards, mobile top ups, eSIM and direct flight and hotel bookings with Bitcoin or Crypto.\",\"how_it_works\":\"How it works\",\"interested_in_buying_gift_cards_with_bitcoin\":\"Interested in buying gift cards with Bitcoin or other Crypto? Or via BinancePay and GatePay. In this guide, we'll walk you through the process of purchasing gift cards and mobile top ups using the power of Bitcoin. Unlock a new realm of possibilities and discover how to leverage your digital assets for real-world purchases.\",\"choose_a_product_from_thousands_of_options\":\"Choose a product from thousands of options\",\"select_the_payment_method\":\"Select the payment method\",\"pay_with_your_preferred_crypto_and_receive_your_product_instantly\":\"Pay with your preferred crypto and receive your product instantly\",\"pay_with_bitcoin_litecoin\":\"Pay with Bitcoin, Litecoin, Ethereum, SOL, TRX, TON, DOGE, WLD, SUI, USDC, USDT, USDC.e, USDT.e, USDS, USDE, PYUSD, EUROC, FDUSD, and DAI on Lightning Network, Ethereum, Polygon, Arbitrum, Avalanche, Optimism, Binance Smart Chain, OKX, Base, Sonic, Plasma, World Chain, Tron, Solana, TON and Sui. BinancePay, Krak, KuCoin Pay GatePay supported.\",\"start_shopping_now\":\"Start shopping now!\",\"easy_and_convenient\":\"Easy and convenient\",\"effortless_and_quick\":\"Effortless and quick\",\"cryptocurrency_allows_easy_purchase_of_gift_cards_offering_a_smooth_and_hassle_free_transaction_process\":\"Cryptocurrency allows easy purchase of gift cards, offering a smooth and hassle-free transaction process.\",\"privacy_and_security\":\"Privacy and security\",\"unlike_traditional_payment_methods_that_require_personal_information\":\"Unlike traditional payment methods that require personal information, cryptocurrency transactions protect user identities and financial data.\",\"wide_selection_of_gift_cards\":\"Wide selection of gift cards\",\"diverse_range_of_gift_card_options\":\"Diverse range of gift card options, ensuring users find the perfect choice for their preferences.\",\"step_1\":\"Step 1\",\"choose_your_preferred_brand\":\"Choose your preferred product\",\"take_your_first_step_by_selecting_the_mobile_top-ups_or_gift_cards_that_align_with_your_preferences\":\"Take your first step by selecting the mobile top ups or gift cards that align with your preferences.\",\"pay_close_attention_to_the_country_you_select_as_different_brands_may_only_work_in_specific_regions_ensure_that_the_brand_you_choose_is_compatible_with_your_desired_country\":\"Pay close attention to the country you select, as different brands may only work in specific regions. Ensure that the brand you choose is compatible with your desired country.\",\"cryptorefills_supports_1000_of_gift_cards_and_mobile_top_ups_in_180_countries\":\"Cryptorefills supports 1000's of gift cards and mobile top ups in 180 countries.\",\"step_2\":\"Step 2\",\"select_the_amount_and_currency\":\"Select the amount and cryptocurrency\",\"choose_the_desired_value_for_the_gift_card_for_certain_products_the_value_is_fixed_while_for_others_it_may_be_within_a_specific_range\":\"Choose the desired value for the gift card. For certain products, the value is fixed, while for others, it may be within a specific range.\",\"by_adjusting_the_currency_in_the_estimated_price_section_you_can_view_the_value_in_your_preferred_currency\":\"By adjusting the currency in the 'Estimated price' section, you can view the value in your preferred currency.\",\"enter_amount\":\"Amount\",\"estimated_price\":\"Estimated price\",\"accepted_coins\":\"Accepted coins\",\"step_3_optional\":\"Step 3 (Optional)\",\"step_3\":\"Step 3\",\"connect_your_wallet_to_pay_with_your_nft_gift_card\":\"Connect your wallet, pay with your programmable gift card\",\"cryptorefills_supports_the_possibility_to_accept_nft_gift_cards_provided_by_the_atomicrails_protocol\":\"Cryptorefills supports the possibility to accept Programmable gift cards provided by the AtomicRails protocol.\",\"nft_gift_cards_are_nfts_that_hold_a_balance_and_can_be_used_by_connecting_your_wallet\":\"Programmable gift cards are NFTs that hold a balance and can be used by connecting your wallet.\",\"applying_the_gift_card_will_initiate_a_transaction_on_the_blockchain_by_executing_this_transaction_you_give_cryptorefills_the_right_to_deduct_the_amount_from_your_nft_gift_card_please_note_that_the_nft_gift_card_can_be_on_a_different_network_than_the_selected_payment_option\":\"Applying the gift card will initiate a transaction on the blockchain. By executing this transaction, you give Cryptorefills the right to deduct the amount from your Programmable gift card. Please note that the Programmable gift card can be on a different network than the selected payment option.\",\"step_4\":\"Step 4\",\"on_chain_binancepay_or_gatepay\":\"On chain, Binance Pay, Krak, Kucoin Pay, Base Pay, or Gate Pay\",\"select_the_preferred_payment_method\":\"Select the preferred payment method\",\"for_blockchain_payments_from_an_exchange_or_wallet\":\"for blockchain payments from an exchange or wallet.\",\"binancepay\":\"BinancePay\",\"to_ensure_a_native_experience_when_using_a_binance_account\":\"to ensure a native experience when using a Binance account.\",\"gatepay\":\"Gate Pay\",\"optimized_user_experience_while_utilizing_a_gatepay_account\":\"optimized user experience while utilizing a GatePay account.\",\"kucoinpay\":\"KuCoin Pay\",\"fast_and_seamless_crypto_transactions_with_kucoin\":\"fast and seamless crypto transactions with KuCoin.\",\"krak\":\"Krak\",\"pay_directly_from_your_Krak\":\"pay directly from your Krak account with full protection and low fees.\",\"basepay\":\"Base Pay\",\"simple_and_secure_payments_with_the_coinbase_ecosystem\":\"simple and secure payments within the Coinbase ecosystem.\",\"step_5\":\"Step 5\",\"select_the_network\":\"Select the network\",\"this_step_is_only_for_on-chain_payments_and_is_not_applicable_to_binancepay_and_gatepay\":\"This step is only for On-Chain payments and is not applicable to BinancePay and GatePay.\",\"this_step_is_only_for_on_chain_payments\":\"This step is only for On-Chain payments and is not applicable to exchanges payments like BinancePay, Gatepay, Krak etc.\",\"coins_such_as_usdc_usdt_dai_and_eth_are_supported_by_cryptorefils_on_multiple_networks_blockchains_make_sure_you_choose_the_network_you_want_to_use\":\"Coins such as USDC, USDT, PYUSD, and ETH are supported by Cryptorefills on multiple networks (blockchains). Make sure you choose the network you want to use.\",\"accepted_networks\":\"Accepted networks\",\"step_6\":\"Step 6\",\"pay_your_purchase\":\"Pay your purchase\",\"on_chain\":\"On-chain\",\"scan_the_qr_code_or_send_the_amount_to_the_wallet_address_mentioned_on_the_payment_page\":\"Scan the QR code or send the amount to the wallet address displayed on the payment page.\",\"scan_the_qr_code_or_send_the_exact_amount\":\"Scan the QR code or send the exact amount to the wallet address displayed on the payment page. Use your preferred wallet (e.g. MetaMask, Phantom, Base, or any compatible on-chain wallet).\",\"open_the_wallet_opens_your_local_wallet_like_metamask_or_electrum\":\"Open the wallet opens your local wallet, like MetaMask, Phantom or Base.\",\"please_pay_close_attention_to_the_selected_network_only_send_coins_on_the_network_you_have_selected\":\"Please pay close attention to the selected network. Only send coins on the network you have selected.\",\"binancepay_/_gatepay\":\"BinancePay / GatePay\",\"exchange_payments\":\"Exchange Payments\",\"if_you_selected_a_payment_method_such_as_binance_pay\":\"If you selected a payment method such as Binance Pay, Gate Pay, KuCoin Pay, Kraken Pay, or Base Pay, simply confirm the payment in your exchange app\",\"open_the_app_and_scan_the_qr_code\":\"Open the app and scan the QR code, or use the “Pay Now” button to be redirected to the exchange’s confirmation page\",\"follow_the_instructions_displayed_in_your_account\":\"Follow the instructions displayed in your account to complete the transaction.\",\"open_your_binance_or_gateio_app_scan_the_qr_code_and_confirm_your_payment\":\"Open your Binance or Gate.io app, scan the QR code, and confirm your payment.\",\"the_pay_now_button_will_redirect_you_to_the_binance_or_gateio_payment_confirmation_page\":\"The \\\"Pay Now\\\" button will redirect you to the Binance or Gate.io payment confirmation page.\",\"step_7\":\"Step 7\",\"enjoy_your_product\":\"Enjoy your product\",\"once_the_transaction_is_confirmed_on_the_blockchain_we_will_deliver_your_order\":\"Once the transaction is confirmed on the blockchain, we will deliver your order to the email address provided in checkout.\",\"you_can_also_see_the_order_status_in_your_account_history\":\"You can also see the order status in your account history. If you don't have an account yet, create an account with the email used in your order to see the status.\",\"completed\":\"Completed\",\"step_8_bonus\":\"Step 8 (Bonus)\",\"earn_points\":\"Earn points\",\"when_you_buy_on_cryptorefills_you_will_automatically_earn_cryptorefills_points_as_soon_as_you_have_enough_points_you_can_redeem_your_points_for_crypto\":\"When you buy on Cryptorefills, you will automatically earn Cryptorefills points. As soon as you have enough points, you can redeem your points for Crypto.\",\"discover_how_to_spend_your_points\":\"Discover how to spend your points\",\"ready_to_shop\":\"Ready to shop?\",\"shop_now\":\"Shop now\",\"note:_some_parts_of_the_html_contain_dynamic_content_eg_icons_and_links_which_may_not_be_represented_accurately_in_the_extracted_text\":\"Note: Some parts of the HTML contain dynamic content (e.g., icons and links), which may not be represented accurately in the extracted text.\"},\"EarnPoints\":{\"title\":\"Collaborate with us and earn points - Cryptorefills\",\"description\":\"Earn Cryptocurrency rewards: unlock exciting benefits with Cryptorefills points.\"},\"Ambassador\":{\"title\":\"Cryptorefills ambassador program\",\"description\":\"Boost your visibility and personal brand and expand your network and connections\"},\"About\":{\"title\":\"About Cryptorefills\",\"description\":\"Cryptorefills is a leading global player in flights, stays, mobile top up and gift card retail for crypto users, headquartered in Amsterdam.\",\"hero\":{\"heading\":\"The real-world commerce layer\",\"heading_span\":\"for digital assets and AI agents.\",\"paragraph\":\"Cryptorefills connects wallets and AI agents to real-world spending with Bitcoin, stablecoins and digital assets across 180+ countries and territories. Gift cards, mobile top up, eSIM, flights and stays, for people and AI agents alike.\",\"cta_browse\":\"Browse brands\",\"cta_api\":\"Explore the API\",\"more_currencies\":\"+20 more\"},\"technology\":{\"heading\":\"We've led every major shift\",\"heading_span\":\"in wallet-based commerce.\",\"footer_status\":\"On branch main · working tree clean.\",\"footer_commits\":\"{count} commits\",\"footer_still_shipping\":\"· still shipping\",\"items\":{\"0\":{\"message\":\"self-process blockchain transactions for ecommerce\",\"detail\":\"First self-sovereign crypto payment processing. No third-party gateway.\"},\"1\":{\"message\":\"add Lightning Network payments for retail\",\"detail\":\"Sub-second Bitcoin payments via the Lightning Network for everyday purchases.\"},\"2\":{\"message\":\"Ethereum L2 + Avalanche stablecoin payments\",\"detail\":\"First ecommerce globally to process Ethereum Layer 2 payments. First to accept stablecoins on Avalanche — a fast-finality ERC-20 chain.\"},\"3\":{\"message\":\"Euro Coin by Circle on day-one of mainnet launch\",\"detail\":\"EURC live on our checkout the same day it went live on Ethereum Mainnet. Bitcoin via Avalanche Bridge also added.\"},\"4\":{\"message\":\"widest L2 stablecoin coverage in ecommerce\",\"detail\":\"Polygon, Optimism, Arbitrum, Tron, Sonic, Solana — the most scalable networks all in one checkout.\"},\"5\":{\"message\":\"add SUI and TON payment networks\",\"detail\":\"SUI and TON join the network lineup, extending coverage to the fastest-growing L1 ecosystems.\"},\"6\":{\"message\":\"MCP server, x402 protocol and native AI agent purchasing\",\"detail\":\"Full MCP server with tool documentation for autonomous agents. Claude, ChatGPT and any x402-compatible agent can search, quote and purchase without a checkout UI.\"},\"7\":{\"message\":\"open reference for agentic commerce\",\"detail\":\"Protocols (ACP, AP2, x402, MCP, L402), stablecoin rails, agent skills and merchant playbooks. The operational layers specs leave out, published as an open repo.\"}}},\"what_we_do\":{\"heading\":\"Where digital assets go to work.\",\"heading_span\":\"For people and AI agents alike.\",\"people_badge\":\"For people\",\"people_heading\":\"Spend Bitcoin, stablecoins and digital assets everywhere it matters.\",\"people_paragraph\":\"300+ airlines, a million-plus hotels, mobile top up in every major market, plus a deep gift card catalog. Paid in Bitcoin, Lightning, or any major stablecoin. No bank account, no extra step.\",\"people_image_alt\":\"Shopping with crypto\",\"people_cta\":\"Browse all brands\",\"agents_badge\":\"For AI agents\",\"agents_heading\":\"Autonomous purchasing, zero friction.\",\"agents_paragraph\":\"AI agents connect directly via our MCP server. Claude, ChatGPT and any x402-compatible agent can search, quote and purchase autonomously. No account opening or bank-style onboarding for standard purchases.\",\"agents_cta\":\"Add as MCP server\"},\"social_proof\":{\"stats\":{\"0\":\"Brands across 180+ countries\",\"1\":\"Delivered in under 10 seconds\",\"2\":\"Live since\"},\"compliance_badge\":\"Compliance\",\"compliance_heading\":\"Regulated transactions since 2022. Payments settle onchain in under a second on Solana, Base, Avalanche and SUI.\",\"compliance_body\":\"Members of \u003cholland_fintech\u003eHolland Fintech Association\u003c/holland_fintech\u003e, \u003cbcnl\u003eBlockchain Netherlands Foundation (BCNL)\u003c/bcnl\u003e and IMA Europe.\",\"compliance_logo_alt\":\"Holland Fintech Association\"},\"research\":{\"pull_quote\":\"The global benchmark for crypto consumer adoption\",\"pull_quote_source\":\"— Cryptorefills Labs Annual Consumer Spending Report\",\"paragraph\":\"Cryptorefills Labs publishes the most detailed research on how people use Bitcoin, stablecoins and digital assets to pay for real things. Our peer-reviewed work tracks how stablecoins have overtaken volatile currencies at the point of purchase, and is cited by leading financial publications worldwide.\",\"cited_by\":\"Cited by\",\"cta\":\"Read the research\",\"key_finding_label\":\"Key finding\",\"key_finding_stat_label\":\"of digital asset buyers prefer stablecoins at point of purchase.\",\"chart_stablecoins\":\"Stablecoins\",\"chart_volatile\":\"Volatile assets\",\"stat_growth_label\":\"Three-year growth\",\"stat_peer_reviewed_label\":\"Peer-reviewed\",\"figcaption\":\"Cryptorefills Labs · Annual Consumer Spending Report\"},\"values\":{\"heading\":\"How we work,\",\"heading_span\":\"and why it matters.\",\"items\":{\"0\":{\"name\":\"Be reliable.\",\"description\":\"Deliver fast, fix what breaks and keep improving the checkout until it works for customers, partners and agents.\"},\"1\":{\"name\":\"Publish what we learn.\",\"description\":\"Cryptorefills Labs turns real spending data into transparent research on how digital assets are used in the real world.\"},\"2\":{\"name\":\"Keep shipping early.\",\"description\":\"We test new rails before they are obvious, from Lightning and stablecoins to MCP, x402 and agentic commerce.\"},\"3\":{\"name\":\"Help people complete the purchase.\",\"description\":\"Support customers, partners and builders when payments, products or integrations need a human hand.\"},\"4\":{\"name\":\"Own the outcome.\",\"description\":\"Handle compliance, risk controls, refunds and issue resolution instead of pushing problems downstream.\"},\"5\":{\"name\":\"Build for the long run.\",\"description\":\"Sustainable teams ship better systems. We protect focus, recovery and the pace needed to keep improving.\"}}},\"cta\":{\"heading\":\"Ready to spend digital assets\",\"heading_span\":\"in the real world?\",\"paragraph\":\"For shoppers, builders and partners. Cryptorefills has the rails.\",\"cards\":{\"0\":{\"badge\":\"Shoppers\",\"heading\":\"Browse the full catalog.\",\"body\":\"Gift cards, flights, hotels, mobile top up. Pay with any major digital asset, no bank account required.\",\"cta\":\"Open the catalog\"},\"1\":{\"badge\":\"Developers\",\"heading\":\"Integrate the API.\",\"body\":\"REST API, MCP server and x402-compatible purchasing flows.\",\"cta\":\"API and MCP docs\"},\"2\":{\"badge\":\"Gift card brands\",\"heading\":\"Partner with us.\",\"body\":\"List your gift card brand on the leading digital asset commerce platform. Zero listing fees, zero setup cost.\",\"cta\":\"Become a partner\"}}}},\"Help\":{\"title\":\"Help - Cryptorefills\",\"description\":\"Search for answers or browse our knowledge base.\",\"how_can_we_help_you\":\"How can we help you?\",\"whether_youve_got_a_question_about_your_order_or_a_product_were_here_to_help_you_out_in_a_way_that_suits_you\":\"Whether you've got a question about your order or a product, we're here to help you out in a way that suits you.\",\"difference_crypto\":\"Different Cryptos\",\"understanding_coins_tokens_networks\":\"Understanding Coins Tokens \u0026 Networks. What are Stablecoins and the role of Networks.\",\"learn_differences\":\"Learn how to use \",\"how_does_it_work\":\"How it works\",\"unsure_how_you_can_buy_a_product\":\"Unsure how you can buy a product? We'll guide you step-by-step through the process.\",\"start_learning\":\"Start learning\",\"more_insights\":\"More insights\",\"get_everything_out_of_your_crypto\":\"Get everything out of your crypto. Find the latest tips on how to use crypto and web3 technologies at Cryptorefills.\",\"discover\":\"Discover\",\"faq\":\"FAQ\",\"read_our_faqs\":\"Read our FAQ's\",\"browse_our_frequently_asked_questions_to_find_answers_to_all_your_cryptorefills_questions\":\"Browse our frequently asked questions to find answers to…ummm frequently asked questions. 🙂\",\"contact_us\":\"Contact us\",\"whether_youve_got_a_question_about_your_order_or_a_product_were_here_to_help_you_out\":\"Have an infrequently asked question? We're here to help you out too.\",\"contact\":\"Contact\",\"your_last_created_orders\":\"Your last created orders\",\"lost_track_of_your_order_creations_and_their_status_see_the_overview_below\":\"Lost track of your order creations and their status? See the overview below!\",\"order_id\":\"Order id\",\"go_to_order\":\"Go to order\",\"no_recently_created_orders_found\":\"No recently created orders found. Please log in to view all orders related to your account.\",\"just_now\":\"just now\",\"minute\":\"minute\",\"minutes\":\"minutes\",\"ago\":\"ago\",\"hour\":\"hour\",\"hours\":\"hours\",\"and\":\"and\",\"day\":\"day\",\"days\":\"days\"},\"Insights\":{\"title\":\"Insights - Cryptorefills\",\"description\":\"Everything from crypto to blockchain technologies.\",\"see_all_insights\":\"See all insights\",\"min_read\":\"Min read\",\"everything_from_crypto_to_blockchain_technologies\":\"Everything from crypto to blockchain technologies\",\"insights\":\"Insights\",\"next\":\"Next\",\"previous\":\"Previous\",\"updated\":\"Updated\",\"search_for_articles\":\"Search for articles\",\"no_articles_found\":\"No articles found for {query}\",\"no_article_in_your_language\":\"No article in your language available at the moment.\",\"discover_articles_in_english\":\"Discover articles in English.\",\"clear_search\":\"Clear search\"},\"Events\":{\"title\":\"Crypto events\",\"description\":\"Discover upcoming blockchain, stablecoin web3 events, conferences and meetups. Get all the key information you need on one place\",\"see_all_events\":\"See all events\",\"crypto_events\":\"Crypto events\",\"discover_upcoming_blockchain\":\"Discover upcoming blockchain, stablecoin web3 events, conferences and meetups. Get all the key information you need on one place.\",\"next\":\"Next\",\"previous\":\"Previous\"},\"Referral\":{\"title\":\"Referral - Cryptorefills\",\"description\":\"Earn more points by inviting friends\",\"earn_points_with_friends\":\"Earn points with your friends\",\"earn_points_description_1\":\"For every friend, you will earn 0.5x of the points they earn at Cryptorefills.\",\"earn_points_description_2\":\"Your friend will also get 1.5x more points on their first order at Cryptorefills. You can get a maximum of 500 points per friend you've invited.\",\"what_are_points_title\":\"What are Cryptorefills points?\",\"what_are_points_description\":\"At Cryptorefills, we believe in rewarding every customer for their purchases. With each transaction, you automatically earn Cryptorefills Points, our unique loyalty points. These points can then be redeemed for Bitcoin, Litecoin (and soon others) directly to your wallet for free.\",\"how_to_join_title\":\"How to join the referral program?\",\"how_to_join_description\":\"To participate in our referral program, simply make a single purchase to activate it for yourself. For your referrals to be eligible within the program, it's important that your friends haven't previously registered an account with Cryptorefills. Additionally, for their purchases to qualify, your friends must complete their initial order by using the invite link you provide them specifically for Cryptorefills.\",\"how_to_invite_title\":\"How to invite friends?\",\"get_invite_link\":\"Get your exclusive invite link\",\"your_unique_referral_link_can_be_found\":\"Your unique referral link can be found in\",\"your_account_details\":\"your account details\",\"invite_friends\":\"Invite friends\",\"invite_friends_description\":\"Share your exclusive invite link with friends on your site, blog, social media or email.\",\"earn_more_points\":\"Earn more points\",\"earn_more_points_description\":\"You will earn 0.5x of the points they will earn from their orders at Cryptorefills.\",\"spread_the_word\":\"Spread the word and start earning!\",\"program_details\":\"Program details\",\"support_invite_multiple\":\"You can invite and earn more points multiple times. The more you promote your invite link the more points you will earn!\",\"support_terms_violation\":\"We can revoke referral program access or deny rewards if we suspect terms violation, abusive activity (like self-referrals, fake accounts, existing users), or harm to Cryptorefills brand.\",\"support_modify_offer\":\"We reserve the right to modify the referral offer at any time. By continuing to invite friends after an update to the terms, you are indicating that you are accepting them.\",\"support_redeem_points\":\"Redeem your points into LTC or BTC coins. Then, use these coins for purchases on Cryptorefills.\",\"unveiling_process_title\":\"Unveiling the process\",\"illustration\":\"Illustration:\",\"unveiling_process_item\":\"Imagine User A extending an invitation to User B. When User B completes a purchase and earns 200 Cryptorefills points, User A is seamlessly credited with 100 Cryptorefills points—equivalent to 0.5 times the points amassed by User B. This cycle continues, with User A consistently earning 0.5 times the Cryptorefills points acquired by User B with each successive purchase.\",\"all_aboard_the_blockchain\":\"All aboard the blockchain\",\"train_next_stop_gift_cards\":\"train 🚀, next stop: gift cards!\",\"so_youre_the_liaison\":\"So you're the liaison\",\"between_the_crypto_world\":\"between the crypto world\",\"and_old_school_retail\":\"and old-school retail?\",\"i_used_bitcoin_to_buy_a_gift\":\"I used Bitcoin to buy a gift\",\"card_on_cryptorefills_now_i\":\"card on Cryptorefills. Now I\",\"can_shop_at_big_brands\":\"can shop at big brands!\",\"exactly_call_me_the_crypto\":\"Exactly, call me the Crypto-\",\"conductor\":\"Conductor!\"},\"Reviews\":{\"title\":\"Cryptorefills reviews\",\"what_our_customers_say\":\"What our customers say\",\"description\":\"Read verified reviews from crypto users who paid for gift cards, mobile topups, eSIMs, flights, and stays. Rated on Trustpilot. No KYC required.\",\"heading\":\"What buyers actually say.\",\"sub_heading\":\"Verified reviews from across the Cryptorefills community.\",\"original\":\"Original\",\"show_translation\":\"Show translation\",\"translated\":\"Translated\",\"show_original\":\"Show original\",\"show_original_lang\":\"Show original ({language})\",\"translate\":\"Translate\",\"read_more\":\"Read more\",\"show_less\":\"Show less\",\"from\":\"from\",\"verified_purchase\":\"Verified purchase\",\"see_all_on_trustpilot\":\"See all reviews on Trustpilot\",\"trusted_by_thousands\":\"Trusted by thousands of crypto users\",\"verified_reviews_count\":\"{count, number}+ verified purchases\",\"top_reviews_title\":\"Latest reviews\",\"top_reviews_subtitle\":\"Out of {count, number}+ verified reviews on Trustpilot.\",\"top_reviews_subtitle_fallback\":\"From our verified reviews on Trustpilot.\",\"all_reviews\":\"All reviews\",\"filter_by\":\"Filter by\",\"kind_giftcards\":\"Gift cards\",\"kind_mobiletopup\":\"Mobile top-ups\",\"kind_esim\":\"eSIM\",\"kind_flights\":\"Flights\",\"kind_stays\":\"Stays\",\"kind_other\":\"Other\",\"reviews_landing_section_label\":\"Trust score and product categories\",\"leave_a_review\":\"Leave a review\",\"leave_a_review_helper\":\"After your next purchase you'll be able to share a verified review.\"},\"VerifiedReview\":{\"share_your_experience\":\"Share your experience\",\"your_review_helps_other_buyers\":\"Your review helps other people decide with confidence.\",\"rate_n_stars\":\"Rate {n} stars\",\"name_optional\":\"Name (optional)\",\"your_name_placeholder\":\"How should we display your name?\",\"review\":\"Review\",\"review_placeholder\":\"Tell other people what worked, what surprised you, what you'd improve.\",\"min_20_chars\":\"Please write at least 20 characters.\",\"submit_review\":\"Submit review\",\"thanks_for_your_review\":\"Thanks for your review!\",\"something_went_wrong\":\"Something went wrong. Please try again.\",\"already_reviewed\":\"You've already reviewed this order.\"},\"Settings\":{\"title\":\"Settings - Cryptorefills\",\"settings\":\"Settings\",\"account\":\"Account\",\"email\":\"Email\",\"password\":\"Password\",\"change_password\":\"Change password\",\"security\":\"Security\",\"error_loading_user_info\":\"Unable to load user information\",\"your_email_has_been_verified\":\"Your email has been verified\",\"provide_full_name\":\"Provide full name\",\"please_enter_your_first_and_lastname_as_written_on_your_id_documents\":\"Please enter your first and lastname as written on your ID documents\",\"first_name\":\"First name\",\"first_name_invalid_characters\":\"First name may only include letters, spaces, hyphens, and apostrophes\",\"first_name_no_spaces\":\"First name cannot be just spaces\",\"first_name_min_length\":\"First name must be at least 1 character\",\"first_name_not_test\":\"First name cannot be \\\"test\\\" or similar\",\"first_name_required\":\"First name is required\",\"last_name\":\"Last name\",\"last_name_invalid_characters\":\"Last name may only include letters, spaces, hyphens, and apostrophes\",\"last_name_no_spaces\":\"Last name cannot be just spaces\",\"last_name_min_length\":\"Last name must be at least 1 character\",\"last_name_not_test\":\"Last name cannot be \\\"test\\\" or similar\",\"last_name_required\":\"Last name is required\",\"submit\":\"Submit\",\"full_name\":\"Full name\",\"identity_verification\":\"Identity verification\",\"connect_x_account\":\"Connect X account\",\"x_account_connected\":\"Account connected\",\"your_account_has_2fa_enabled\":\"Your account has 2FA enabled\",\"your_account_does_not_have_2fa_enabled\":\"Your account does not have 2FA enabled\",\"kyc_not_verified\":\"Your KYC is not verified\",\"disconnect_x_account\":\"Disconnect X account\",\"twitter_account\":\"𝕏 account\",\"enter_full_name\":\"Enter full name\",\"pending\":\"Pending\",\"verified\":\"Verified\",\"enable\":\"Enable\",\"active\":\"Active\",\"lets_see_if_this_works\":\"Lets see if this works {name}\",\"complete_verification\":\"Complete verification\",\"account_type\":\"Account type\",\"basic\":\"Basic\",\"pending_review\":\"Pending review\",\"manage_your_account_security_and_developer_access\":\"Manage your account, security, and developer access.\",\"personal_info\":\"Personal info\",\"personal_info_description\":\"How you appear on receipts and in our records.\",\"two_factor_authentication\":\"Two-factor authentication\",\"security_description\":\"Protect your account with a password and second factor.\",\"identity\":\"Identity\",\"identity_description\":\"Verify your identity to raise purchase limits.\",\"developer\":\"Developer\",\"developer_description\":\"Use your Partner ID to attribute API traffic and earn referral commissions.\",\"open_integration_guide\":\"Open integration guide\",\"partner_id\":\"Partner ID\"},\"BalanceChecker\":{\"title\":\"Check {brand} gift card balance | remaining funds - Cryptorefills\",\"description\":\"Easily check your {brand} gift card balance and stay informed about your remaining funds. Ensure you're always updated on your available credit with Cryptorefills.\",\"check_brand_gift_card_balance\":\"Check {brand} gift card balance\",\"easily_check_your_brand_gift_card_balance_by_visiting_the_official_brand_website_online\":\"Easily check your {brand} gift card balance by visiting the official {brand} website online.\",\"looking_to_buy_a_brand_gift_card\":\"Looking to buy a {brand} gift card? You can purchase one instantly using Bitcoin or other cryptocurrencies by clicking the button below.\",\"check_balance\":\"Check balance\",\"buy_brand_gift_card\":\"Buy {brand} gift card\",\"you_will_be_redirected_to_website\":\"You will be redirected to {website}\",\"about_cryptorefills\":\"About Cryptorefills\",\"cryptorefills_is_a_leading_global_platform_that_allows_you_to\":\"Cryptorefills is a leading global platform that allows you to purchase gift cards, mobile top-ups, eSIMs, flights, and hotel stays using cryptocurrencies like Bitcoin, Ethereum, USDT, and USDC. By bridging the gap between the crypto world and everyday services, we enable you to spend your crypto on real-world goods seamlessly.\",\"our_platform_supports_a_wide_range_of_cryptocurrencies_and\":\"Our platform supports a wide range of cryptocurrencies and blockchain networks, including Lightning Network, Avalanche, Polygon, Solana, Tron, Base, Binance Chain, World Chain, Ton and Arbitrum. With Cryptorefills, you can:\",\"buy_gift_cards_with_bitcoin_and_crypto\":\"Buy gift cards with Bitcoin and Crypto\",\"access_thousands_of_gift_cards_from_popular_brands_worldwide\":\"Access thousands of gift cards from popular brands worldwide.\",\"recharge_mobile_phones\":\"Recharge mobile phones:\",\"top_up_your_or_someone_elses_mobile_phone_instantly_using_crypto\":\"Top up your or someone else's mobile phone instantly using crypto.\",\"book_flights_and_hotels\":\"Book flights and hotels:\",\"pay_for_flights_and_accommodations_globally_with_your_preferred_cryptocurrency\":\"Pay for flights and accommodations globally with your preferred cryptocurrency.\",\"purchase_esims\":\"Purchase eSIMs:\",\"stay_connected_while_traveling_without_the_hassle_of_physical_sim_cards\":\"Stay connected while traveling without the hassle of physical SIM cards.\",\"join_us_and_unlock_the_full_potential_of_your_cryptocurrencies_today\":\"Join us and unlock the full potential of your cryptocurrencies today.\",\"buy_other_gift_cards_with_crypto\":\"Buy other gift cards with crypto\"},\"Explanations\":{\"which_network_to_select\":\"Which network\",\"make_sure_to_select_the_correct_network_avoid_mistakes\":\"Make sure to select the correct network, avoid mistakes.\",\"a_network_in_crypto\":\"A \\\"network\\\" in crypto is the specific blockchain (e.g., Ethereum, Binance Smart Chain, Polygon) your transaction runs on, and sending to the wrong one can lead to lost or uncredited funds.\",\"when_making_your_payment_in_a_stablecoin\":\"When making your payment in a stablecoin (such as USDT), please ensure that you use the exact same network you select on our checkout page.\",\"example\":\"Example\",\"if_you_choose_usdt_on_the_polygon\":\"If you choose USDT on the Polygon (MATIC) network, you must send your payment from Polygon, not from any other network (such as BNB Smart Chain or Ethereum mainnet).\"},\"Survey\":{\"title\":\"Why People Choose Cryptorefills | Customer Experience Survey\",\"description\":\"Tell us why you chose Cryptorefills and help us build a better crypto shopping experience with a few short questions.\",\"why_did_you_choose_cryptorefills\":\" Why did you choose Cryptorefills?\",\"in_just_5_quick_questions\":\"In a few quick questions, you'll help us understand why people choose Cryptorefills and how we can make your experience even better.\",\"your_answers_help_shape_new_features\":\"Your answers help shape new features, smoother payments, and a better crypto shopping journey.\",\"what_was_the_1\":\"What was the #1 thing Cryptorefills did better than anywhere else in today's purchase?\",\"example_checkout_accepted_my_wallet_instantly\":\"Example: ‘Checkout accepted my wallet instantly\",\"At_what_exact_step_did_you\":\"At what exact step did you hesitate, and what made you hesitate?\",\"example_i_got_confused_about_how_to_make_a_crypto_payment_from_my_wallet\":\"Example: I got confused about how to make a crypto payment from my wallet.\",\"think_about_that_rating\":\"Think about that rating. Which specific experience or feature influenced it most?\",\"example_the_payment_was_fast_and_smoot\":\"Example: The payment was fast and smooth, and I liked that I didn't need to create an account to complete my order.\",\"how_your_experience_with_cryptorefills_so_far\":\"How's your experience with Cryptorefills so far?\",\"oops_something_went_wrong_with_our_feedback_collection\":\"Oops, something went wrong with our feedback collection\",\"our_engineers_have_been_informed\":\"Our engineers have been informed and are working on a solution. Thank you for your understanding.\",\"thank_you_for_sharing_your_feedback_with_us\":\"Thank you for sharing your feedback with us!\",\"we_use_your_feedback_to_shape_new_features\":\"We use your feedback to shape new features and make Cryptorefills even more useful for you.\",\"just_5_quick_questions_to_understand\":\"Just a few quick questions to understand what matters most to you. It only takes about 1 minute.\",\"rate_your_experience\":\"Rate your experience\",\"next_question\":\"Next\",\"this_will_only_take_minute\":\"This will only take 1–2 minute\",\"crypto_usage_mini_survey\":\"Crypto usage mini-survey\",\"help_us_improve_your_experience_takes_about_1_minute\":\"Help us improve your experience. Takes about 1 minute\",\"question_of_total\":\"Question {step} of {total}\",\"please_specify\":\"Please specify\",\"sections\":{\"onboarding\":{\"title\":\"Discovery\"},\"usage\":{\"title\":\"Purchase intent\"},\"networks\":{\"title\":\"Networks\"},\"barriers_motivation\":{\"title\":\"Barriers \u0026 motivation\"},\"purchase_behavior\":{\"title\":\"Checkout experience\"},\"optional_feedback\":{\"title\":\"Optional follow-up\"}},\"questions\":{\"why_paid_with_crypto\":{\"question\":\"Why did you choose to pay with crypto today?\",\"options\":{\"convenience\":\"Convenience\",\"lower_fees\":\"Lower fees\",\"faster\":\"Faster\",\"better_rates\":\"Better conversion rates\",\"privacy\":\"Privacy\",\"no_bank_card\":\"No bank card\",\"rewards_points\":\"Earn points/rewards\",\"habit\":\"Habit\",\"other\":\"Other\"}},\"crypto_acquisition_source\":{\"question\":\"How did you get most of the crypto used for this purchase?\",\"options\":{\"salary_income\":\"Salary or income paid in crypto\",\"trading_profits\":\"Trading profits\",\"staking_yield\":\"Staking or yield rewards\",\"mining\":\"Mining\",\"gambling_winnings\":\"Gambling winnings\",\"bought_on_exchange\":\"Bought on an exchange\",\"p2p_purchase\":\"P2P purchase\",\"gift_from_someone\":\"Gift from someone\",\"other\":\"Other\",\"prefer_not_to_say\":\"Prefer not to say\"}},\"checkout_ease\":{\"question\":\"How easy was checkout today?\",\"options\":{\"very_easy\":\"Very easy\",\"easy\":\"Easy\",\"okay\":\"Okay\",\"difficult\":\"Difficult\",\"very_difficult\":\"Very difficult\"}},\"biggest_challenge\":{\"question\":\"What slowed you down the most? (select all that apply)\",\"options\":{\"checkout_confusing\":\"Checkout steps were confusing\",\"network_coin_confusing\":\"Choosing the right coin/network was confusing\",\"payment_confirmation_slow\":\"Payment confirmation took too long\",\"delivery_slow\":\"Delivery took too long\",\"couldnt_find_product\":\"I couldn't quickly find the product I wanted\",\"trust_not_clear\":\"I wanted clearer trust/safety information\",\"prices_not_clear\":\"Price, fees, or rate breakdown was not clear\",\"other\":\"Other\"}},\"discovery_source_today\":{\"question\":\"Where did you hear about us for this purchase?\",\"options\":{\"binance_app\":\"Binance app\",\"world_app\":\"World App\",\"cryptorefills_app\":\"Cryptorefills iOS/Android app\",\"google_search\":\"Google search\",\"chatgpt_ai\":\"ChatGPT or other AI\",\"wallet_exchange\":\"Wallet or exchange app\",\"trustpilot\":\"Trustpilot\",\"social_reddit_x_youtube\":\"Social (Reddit/X/YouTube)\",\"friend_referral\":\"Friend/referral\",\"other\":\"Other\"}},\"did_buy_intended\":{\"question\":\"Did you buy what you intended to buy today?\",\"options\":{\"yes_exactly\":\"Yes, exactly\",\"partly\":\"Partly\",\"no\":\"No\"}},\"what_was_missing\":{\"question\":\"What was missing? (select all that apply)\",\"options\":{\"brands_or_products\":\"Brands or products I wanted\",\"denominations_or_amounts\":\"Denominations or amounts I needed\",\"country_or_region_availability\":\"Availability in my country/region\",\"payment_options\":\"Coin/network payment options\",\"prices_or_fees\":\"Better prices or lower fees\",\"unclear_checkout_flow\":\"Clearer checkout flow\"}},\"what_else_hoped_to_buy\":{\"question\":\"What else were you hoping to buy? (optional)\"},\"crypto_spend_ratio\":{\"question\":\"What percentage of your crypto income do you typically spend?\",\"options\":{\"mostly_hold\":\"0–10%\",\"hold_more_than_spend\":\"10–30%\",\"spend_and_hold_equal\":\"30–60%\",\"mostly_spend\":\"60%+\"}},\"next_purchase_intent_30d\":{\"question\":\"How likely are you to buy again in the next 30 days?\",\"options\":{\"very_likely\":\"Very likely\",\"likely\":\"Likely\",\"maybe\":\"Maybe\",\"unlikely\":\"Unlikely\"}},\"return_blocker\":{\"question\":\"What would most increase your likelihood to return?\",\"options\":{\"better_prices\":\"Better prices or rates\",\"more_products\":\"More products/brands\",\"easier_checkout\":\"Simpler checkout\",\"faster_payment_confirmation\":\"Faster payment confirmation\",\"more_payment_options\":\"More coin/network options\",\"more_trust_signals\":\"More trust/safety proof\",\"better_loyalty_rewards\":\"Better loyalty rewards\",\"other\":\"Other\"}},\"requested_products\":{\"question\":\"Any product or brand you want us to add? (optional)\"},\"country_adoption_comment\":{\"question\":\"Any comments about crypto adoption in your country?\"},\"interview_opt_in\":{\"question\":\"Would you be open to a short follow-up interview about your purchase experience?\",\"options\":{\"yes\":\"Yes, you can contact me\",\"no\":\"No, I prefer not to be contacted\"}},\"interview_contact\":{\"question\":\"If yes, please leave your preferred contact (email, Telegram, or X handle)\"}}},\"TrustAndSafety\":{\"cryptorefills_trust_safety_secure\":\"Cryptorefills Trust \u0026 Safety: Secure Global Ecommerce for Gift Cards, Flights, and Crypto Top-ups\",\"cryptorefills_trust_and_safety\":\"Cryptorefills Trust and Safety hub details our verified platform reliability, pioneering technology, and secure transaction data for global e-commerce using Bitcoin, Ethereum, and Layer 2 networks.\",\"trust_and_safety_hub\":\"Trust and safety hub\",\"see_why_shoppers_from\":\"See why shoppers from 180+ countries and territories shop with Cryptorefills\",\"at_cryptorefills_we_prioritize_transparency\":\"At Cryptorefills, we prioritize transparency, security, and fast transactions. Our platform ensures customers worldwide can make secure cryptocurrency purchases with confidence and ease.\",\"pioneering_secure_blockchain_payments\":\"Pioneering secure blockchain payments: Cryptorefills history and innovation\",\"we_conducted_our_first\":\"We conducted our first test transaction in July 2018, purchasing a Vodafone mobile credit top-up using X BTC.\",\"the_blockchain_record_of\":\"The blockchain record of that transaction is:\",\"cryptorefills_officially_went_live\":\"Cryptorefills officially went live on July 19th, 2018.\",\"initial_offerings_included\":\"Initial offerings included Mobile Credit top-ups across 600 mobile operators from more than 180 countries, accepting Bitcoin and Litecoin payments.\",\"by_january_2019_we\":\"By January 2019, we added the first gift card catalogue to our offer.\",\"trust_our_customers\":\"Trust our customers\",\"trust_our_transaction_data\":\"Trust our transaction data\",\"transactions_in_the_last\":\"Transactions in the last 2 hours\",\"average_transactions_in_the_last\":\"Average number of transactions in the last 2 hours\",\"top_products_purchased_in\":\"Top products purchased in the last 24 hours\",\"products_delivered_in_less\":\"Products delivered in less than 10 seconds\",\"over_the_past_2\":\"Over the past 2 hours\",\"average_payment_completed_time\":\"Average payment completed time by network\",\"network_bitcoin\":\"Bitcoin\",\"network_ethereum\":\"Ethereum\",\"network_tron\":\"Tron\",\"network_litecoin\":\"Litecoin\",\"network_solana\":\"Solana\",\"network_base\":\"Base\",\"network_polygon\":\"Polygon\",\"network_avalanche\":\"Avalanche\",\"network_sui\":\"SUI\",\"network_ton\":\"TON\",\"trust_our_customer_support\":\"Trust our customer support metrics\",\"average_customer_care_first\":\"Average customer care first response time\",\"average_customer_care_full\":\"Average customer care full ticket resolution time\",\"order_help_text\":\"If you are having trouble with your order, please \u003cfaqLink\u003eread our customer support FAQs\u003c/faqLink\u003e and then \u003ccontactLink\u003eget in touch with us\u003c/contactLink\u003e.\",\"essential_security_rules_for\":\"Essential security rules for secure crypto transactions\",\"rule_1_extensions\":\"Rule #1: Extensions\",\"only_install_what_you\":\"Only install what you need\",\"fake_free_purchase_extensions\":\"Fake free purchase extensions steal crypto and seed phrases. Bookmark cryptorefills.com or install the Cryptorefills Android or iOS app. Never install browser add-ons that claim to give discounts.\",\"rule_2_phishing\":\"Rule #2: Phishing\",\"we_will_never_ask\":\"We will never ask you your seed phrase\",\"scam_emails_copy_our\":\"Scam emails copy our logo. Real messages come from @cryptorefills.com and never contain links asking for keys or wallet approval.\",\"rule_3_verify\":\"Rule #3: Verify\",\"double_check_the_details\":\"Double-check the details at checkout\",\"make_sure_the_wallet\":\"Make sure the wallet address is correct and that you are paying the exact amount requested, with the correct token and network as indicated in the payment page.\",\"rule_4_impersonators\":\"Rule #4: Impersonators\",\"only_trust_verified_social\":\"Only trust verified social media accounts\",\"telegram_twitter_scammers_offer\":\"Telegram / Twitter scammers offer support. Our ONLY official channels are listed at the bottom of this page.\",\"strategic_partnerships_and_media\":\"Strategic partnerships and media recognition\",\"key_partnerships_and_integrations\":\"Key Partnerships and Integrations\",\"financial_partner_since_2022\":\"Financial partner since 2022\",\"financial_partner_since_2022_providing\":\"Financial partner since 2022, providing services directly inside the wallet. Bitget Wallet collaborated with Cryptorefills to enable cryptocurrency payments for travel services in over 100 countries.\",\"first_merchant_in_the\":\"First merchant in the world to accept Krak pay payments (June 2025).\",\"kraken_description\":\"Pay directly from your Kraken account on Cryptorefills.\",\"okx_description\":\"OKX Chain network available, enabling stablecoin payments at checkout.\",\"powering_the_world_top\":\"Powering the World Top ups and gift cards Mini Apps. This integration enables everyday spending for nearly 15 million users.\",\"enabling_kucoin_offchain_payments\":\"Enabling Kucoin offchain payments for Kucoin customers. 41M+ KuCoin users can now spend crypto on flights, hotels, gift cards, and more with Cryptorefills KuCoin Pay.\",\"ton_network_integration\":\"Integrated into the TON ecosystem since 2025.\",\"base_network_integration_available\":\"Base network integration available.\",\"since_2022_processing_transactions\":\"Since 2022 processing transactions for regulated products or services.\",\"cryptorefills_launches_coinbase_pay\":\"Cryptorefills launches Coinbase Pay for Travel Bookings, allowing travelers to pay directly from their Coinbase account.\",\"in_2019_we_began\":\"In 2019, we began processing Lightning Network payments.\",\"unmatched_crypto_ecommerce_technology\":\"Unmatched crypto Ecommerce technology and scalability\",\"we_are_dedicated_to\":\"We are dedicated to the evolution of our technology.\",\"first_e_commerce_in_the_world_to_process_ethereum\":\"First Ecommerce in the world to process Ethereum Layer 2 payments.\",\"self_processing_first_blockchain\":\" Self-processing first blockchain transactions (bitcoin).\",\"processing_lightning_network\":\"Processing Lightning Network payments.\",\"first_e_commerce_in_the_world_to_offer_stablecoin_payments\":\"First Ecommerce in the world to offer stablecoin payments on an Erc20 compatible fast finality blockchain (via Avalanche).\",\"first_e_commerce_in_the_world_to_accept_Bitcoin_via_the_Avalanche\":\"First Ecommerce in the world to accept Bitcoin via the Avalanche Bridge.\",\"first_e_commerce_platform_in_the_world_to_accept_Euro_Coin\":\"First Ecommerce platform in the world to accept Euro Coin by Circle. Launched on the same day EURC went live on Mainnet\",\"only_e_commerce_in_the_world_to_offer_the_widest_range\":\"Only Ecommerce in the world to offer the widest range of Layer 2 and scalable networks for stablecoins, including Polygon, Optimism, Arbitrum, Tron, Sonic, and Solana.\",\"additional_networks_added\":\"Additional networks added such as SUI and TON. MCP server launched, enabling AI agents to discover products and complete purchases.\",\"plasma_network_integration\":\"Plasma network integration added. x402 payments launched, allowing AI agents to autonomously settle purchases using USDC.\",\"verified_customer_trust_and\":\"Verified Customer Trust and Platform Performance Data\",\"customer_trust_metrics\":\"Customer Trust Metrics\",\"our_bayesian_confidence_interval\":\"Our Bayesian confidence interval is 4.6/5 from 374 reviews, which implies a true mean ≥ 4.52 with 95% certainty.\",\"operational_efficiency\":\"Operational Efficiency\",\"of_products_are\":\"96.6% of products are delivered in less than 10 seconds.\",\"average_payment_completed_time_by\":\"Average payment completed time by network (last 6 hours):\",\"customer_support_metrics\":\"Customer Support Metrics\",\"the_worlds_largest_catalogue\":\"The World's largest catalogue available for purchase with cryptocurrency\",\"cryptorefills_consolidates_the_worlds\":\"Cryptorefills consolidates the world's largest catalogue of products and services available for purchase with cryptocurrency.\",\"through_our_aggregate_supplier\":\"Through our aggregate supplier network, we source +6200 individual SKUs.\",\"our_catalogue_includes\":\"Our catalogue includes +6k gift card SKUs from +180 countries and territories.\",\"we_aggregate_mobile_airtime\":\"We aggregate mobile airtime and data top ups from +600 mobile operators worldwide.\",\"we_launched_esim_products\":\"We launched eSim products in 2023.\",\"we_launched_flights_and\":\"We launched flights and hotel bookings in 2024, including 300 airline bookings and +1m hotel and stays properties.\",\"our_suppliers_ensure_maximum_quality\":\"Our suppliers ensure maximum quality, availability of local brands, and multiple backups for stock.\",\"what_the_media_says\":\"What the media says about us\",\"cryptorefills_launches_coinbase_pay_for\":\"Cryptorefills launches Coinbase Pay for Travel Bookings\",\"with_this_integration_travellers\":\"With this integration, travellers can pay directly from their Coinbase account with just a few clicks…\",\"cryptorefills_partners_with_bitget_wallet\":\"Cryptorefills partners with Bitget Wallet to enable crypto travel payments\",\"travellers_will_now_be_able_to\":\"Travellers will now be able to book flights, hotels, and other services using Bitcoin, Ethereum, USDT, USDC, and more.\",\"cryptorefills_launches_x402_payments\":\"Cryptorefills launches x402 payments for AI agents, publishes agentic commerce reference\",\"cryptorefills_launches_x402_and_agentic_reference\":\"AI agents can now settle stablecoin purchases autonomously, alongside an open-source operations reference for developers building agentic commerce.\",\"cryptorefills_enables_x402_payments_for_ai_agents\":\"Cryptorefills enables x402 payments for AI agents at checkout\",\"cryptorefills_enables_x402\":\"Autonomous software can now pay for gift cards, mobile top-ups and eSIMs using USDC on Base in a single programmatic exchange.\",\"cryptorefills_launches_kucoin_pay\":\"Cryptorefills launches Kucoin Pay for Travel Bookings\",\"kucoin_users_can_now\":\"41M+ KuCoin users can now spend crypto on flights, hotels, gift cards, and more with Cryptorefills KuCoin Pay\",\"bitget_wallet_partners_with\":\"Bitget Wallet Partners with Cryptorefills – Enables Crypto Travel Payments in over 100 Countries\",\"bitget_wallet_a_leading\":\"Bitget Wallet, a leading Web3 multi-chain wallet, has announced a strategic partnership with Cryptorefills, to enable cryptocurrency payments for travel services\",\"from_booking_to_boarding\":\"From booking to boarding: how fintech is reshaping travel payments in 2025\",\"bitget_wallet_collaborated_with\":\"Bitget Wallet collaborated with Cryptorefills, enabling users to book flights, hotels, and other services using Bitcoin, Ethereum, USDT\",\"cryptorefills_launches_two_new\":\"Cryptorefills launches two new mini apps within the World App\",\"cryptorefills_aims_to_support\":\"Cryptorefills aims to support over 23 million World App users globally in booking flights and hotels using Worldcoin (WLD)…\",\"cryptorefills_powers_new_mini\":\"Cryptorefills Powers New Mini App within World App, Enabling Everyday Spending for Nearly 15 Million Users\",\"through_this_integration_world\":\"Through this integration, World has launched two Mini Apps powered by Cryptorefills within World App that leverage Cryptorefills global gift card and mobile top up catalogue\",\"ready_to_shop_safely\":\"Ready to shop safely with crypto?\",\"start_shopping\":\"Start Shopping\"},\"AiAgents\":{\"title\":\"AI agents for gift cards and mobile top ups, pay in crypto | Cryptorefills\",\"description\":\"Let Claude, ChatGPT or any MCP agent buy gift cards, mobile top ups and eSIMs with stablecoins or other crypto. No KYC. No account. Works with x402.\",\"hero_title\":\"Buy gift cards, mobile top ups and eSIMs with AI agents.\",\"hero_title_highlight\":\"Pay in stablecoins\",\"hero_description\":\"Let Claude, ChatGPT or any MCP agent buy gift cards, mobile top ups and eSIMs with crypto. No KYC. No account. Works with x402.\",\"video_not_supported\":\"Your browser does not support the video tag.\",\"video_pause\":\"Pause hero animation\",\"video_play\":\"Play hero animation\",\"hero_cta_connect_claude\":\"Connect Claude via MCP\",\"hero_cta_see_methods\":\"See all methods\",\"skills_title\":\"Skills included\",\"skills_description\":\"Traditional APIs need your code to call endpoints. MCP lets an AI agent do that for you: same catalog, same checkout, less glue code.\u003cbr\u003e\u003c/br\u003eRunning \u003ccode\u003enpx skills add cryptorefills/agents\u003c/code\u003e installs three skills over one MCP connection.\",\"skill_catalog_label\":\"Catalog\",\"skill_catalog_summary\":\"Read-only product discovery across 6,600+ brands in 180+ countries. Search by brand, country or category in 15 languages.\",\"skill_buy_label\":\"Create order\",\"skill_buy_summary\":\"Full purchase lifecycle in one connection: search, price, validate, order, pay and track delivery. Bitcoin, Lightning, Ethereum, Solana, USDC, USDT and 15+ other coins.\",\"skill_x402_label\":\"x402\",\"skill_x402_summary\":\"Walletless agent commerce on x402. EIP-712 signed payments, no gas, no API keys. USDC on Base and a signing key, nothing else.\",\"skill_x402_base_description\":\"On Base, x402 uses EIP-712-signed USDC through the \u003clink\u003emain endpoint\u003c/link\u003e.\",\"skill_x402_solana_description\":\"On Solana, x402 uses ed25519-signed USDC through a \u003clink\u003ededicated subdomain\u003c/link\u003e.\",\"connect_title\":\"Connect via MCP\",\"connect_description\":\"One MCP server, every major client. Pick a setup path and copy the snippet.\",\"connect_quick_setup\":\"One-click setup\",\"connect_tablist_label\":\"Connection methods\",\"copy_snippet\":\"Copy snippet\",\"copied\":\"Copied\",\"automation_title\":\"Already live.\",\"automation_subtitle\":\"Four flows agents are wiring up today.\",\"automation_item_1_title\":\"Buy tab in any wallet\",\"automation_item_1\":\"Add a buy tab. The agent quotes live, signs, drops the voucher in-app.\",\"automation_item_1_outcome\":\"Voucher in-wallet, ~3s\",\"automation_item_2_title\":\"Telegram /buy command\",\"automation_item_2\":\"/buy amazon 50, confirm, code in DM. Validation and delivery handled.\",\"automation_item_2_outcome\":\"Conversational, no web UI\",\"automation_item_3_title\":\"DAO rewards as gift cards\",\"automation_item_3\":\"Convert governance points to gift cards. Policy caps spend per member, per month.\",\"automation_item_3_outcome\":\"Onchain in, offchain out\",\"automation_item_4_title\":\"Treasury on autopilot\",\"automation_item_4\":\"Bulk gift cards in stablecoins, on a schedule. Every line signed and reconciled.\",\"automation_item_4_outcome\":\"Bulk, fully audited\",\"openclaw_title\":\"Implementing with OpenClaw\",\"openclaw_description\":\"Orchestrate Cryptorefills tool calls with \u003copenclaw\u003eopenclaw.ai\u003c/openclaw\u003e: deterministic step boundaries, explicit failure handling.\",\"openclaw_cta\":\"See implementation details\",\"hermes_title\":\"Try it with Hermes\",\"hermes_description\":\"Run live prompts against the Cryptorefills MCP via \u003chermes\u003ehermes-agent.nousresearch.com\u003c/hermes\u003e, the hosted agent from Nous Research.\",\"hermes_cta\":\"Open Hermes Agent\",\"integrations_title\":\"Two ways in\",\"integrations_subtitle\":\"Pick the one that fits your agent.\",\"integrations_human_badge\":\"For humans · MCP\",\"integrations_human_chat_aria\":\"Example MCP conversation\",\"integrations_human_speaker_bot\":\"Assistant: \",\"integrations_human_speaker_user\":\"You: \",\"integrations_human_mode_label\":\"Interaction mode\",\"integrations_human_mode_prompt\":\"Prompt\",\"integrations_human_mode_elicitation\":\"Elicitation\",\"integrations_human_prompt_heading\":\"Tell it once.\",\"integrations_human_prompt_body\":\"Drop the full request in one prompt; the agent picks, pays, delivers.\",\"integrations_human_elicitation_heading\":\"Confirm as you go.\",\"integrations_human_elicitation_body\":\"Your AI walks you through it: ask, confirm, done.\",\"integrations_human_cta\":\"Connect via MCP\",\"integrations_bot_badge\":\"For bots · Skills\",\"integrations_bot_heading\":\"Run end-to-end.\",\"integrations_bot_body\":\"One install. The agent picks, pays, returns the voucher.\",\"integrations_bot_cta\":\"View on GitHub\",\"openapi_title\":\"OpenAPI spec\",\"openapi_description\":\"Machine-readable definition of every product, price, and endpoint.\",\"faq_aria_label\":\"FAQ: AI agents and crypto payments\",\"faq_title\":\"FAQ: AI agents and crypto payments\",\"faq_description\":\"How Claude, ChatGPT and other MCP agents use Cryptorefills to pay in stablecoins.\",\"faq_1_question\":\"How do AI agents buy gift cards with crypto?\",\"faq_1_answer\":\"AI agents connect to the Cryptorefills MCP server and use structured tool calls to discover a brand, pick a denomination, validate the order and pay in stablecoins or Bitcoin. No checkout UI, no forms to fill. Once the onchain payment is confirmed, the agent receives the delivery code or voucher.\",\"faq_2_question\":\"Which AI agents support Cryptorefills MCP?\",\"faq_2_answer\":\"Any MCP-compatible agent can connect to Cryptorefills. That includes Claude (via Claude Desktop, Claude Code or the Claude Agent SDK), ChatGPT (via the OpenAI MCP connector) and custom agents built on those SDKs. The server is published at https://api.cryptorefills.com/mcp/http: no API key or account required.\",\"faq_3_question\":\"Does Cryptorefills work with Claude and ChatGPT?\",\"faq_3_answer\":\"Yes. Cryptorefills is a native MCP provider and works with Claude and ChatGPT out of the box. A user can say \\\"buy me a $50 Amazon gift card with USDC on Solana\\\" and the agent handles discovery, pricing, order creation and payment end-to-end.\",\"faq_4_question\":\"What is the x402 payment protocol?\",\"faq_4_answer\":\"x402 is an open HTTP-native payment standard that reuses the 402 Payment Required status code to let clients pay for an API call or product in stablecoins. Cryptorefills supports x402, so AI agents can transact autonomously in a single HTTP round-trip: no connected wallet, no human checkout, no manual confirmation.\",\"faq_5_question\":\"Can I use an AI agent to top up a mobile number?\",\"faq_5_answer\":\"Yes. Through the Cryptorefills MCP, an agent can look up mobile operators for any supported country, pick a top up amount and pay in crypto.\"},\"ApiDocs\":{\"title\":\"Stablecoin checkout API gift cards \u0026 mobile top ups | Cryptorefills\",\"description\":\"Integrate Cryptorefills via REST or MCP. Quote, validate and deliver 6,600+ gift cards, mobile top-ups and eSIMs paid in USDC or USDT. No prefunding. No KYC for your users.\",\"hero_heading\":\"The stablecoin checkout API for gift cards, mobile top-ups and eSIMs\",\"hero_subheading\":\"Use stablecoins like USDC and USDT on fast chains like Solana, Base to move from quote to delivery in a single deterministic flow. Issue inventory at checkout time instead of pre-buying stock, so your working capital stays flexible.\",\"hero_cta_open_dev_docs\":\"Open developer docs\",\"hero_cta_talk_partnerships\":\"Talk to partnerships\",\"benefit_cashflow_title\":\"Cashflow efficient\",\"benefit_cashflow_body\":\"Issue inventory at checkout time instead of pre-buying stock. Keep working capital available for growth.\",\"benefit_settlement_title\":\"Fast settlement UX\",\"benefit_settlement_body\":\"Stablecoin rails plus stream updates reduce waiting friction from payment to delivery.\",\"benefit_web3_fit_title\":\"Web3 user-agent fit\",\"benefit_web3_fit_body\":\"Natural for wallets, mini apps, and agentic checkout flows where users already hold stablecoins.\",\"benefit_operational_control_title\":\"Operational control\",\"benefit_operational_control_body\":\"Check the order before creating it, track each status clearly, and switch to polling if streaming is not available.\",\"payment_overview_title\":\"Pay with your preferred coin\",\"payment_overview_description\":\"Every gift card, top-up, and eSIM in our catalog can be purchased with the coins and networks below.\",\"payment_overview_coins\":\"Coins\",\"payment_overview_networks\":\"Networks\",\"delivery_disclosure_title\":\"Delivery and disclosure requirements\",\"delivery_disclosure_description\":\"To maintain quality during API implementation, please note the following.\",\"notice_valid_email_title\":\"Valid end-user email is required\",\"notice_valid_email_body\":\"Cryptorefills delivers product information to the user. Invalid email means failed delivery experience.\",\"notice_delivery_title\":\"Cryptorefills handles delivery\",\"notice_delivery_body\":\"Cryptorefills is responsible for product delivery at all times in this flow.\",\"notice_service_disclosure_title\":\"Service disclosure to users\",\"notice_service_disclosure_body\":\"Your UX should clearly communicate that the user is making use of Cryptorefills service.\",\"notice_support_title\":\"Customer support from Cryptorefills\",\"notice_support_body\":\"Cryptorefills is available to support customers with questions related to the products they ordered.\",\"partners_section_highlight\":\"Power your platform with a stablecoin offramp via Cryptorefills.\",\"partners_section_body\":\"Join integrated partners enabling real-world crypto spending through a single API.\",\"builders_title\":\"Why it works for builders\",\"builder_rest_title\":\"Clean REST endpoints or MCP\",\"builder_rest_body\":\"Search, price, validate, and create orders through clean REST endpoints or connect via MCP for AI agent workflows.\",\"builder_coins_title\":\"15+ coins across major networks\",\"builder_coins_body\":\"Supports 15+ coins across Solana, Base, Arbitrum, Polygon, Lightning, and more.\",\"builder_catalog_title\":\"6,600+ brands, 180+ countries\",\"builder_catalog_body\":\"Global catalog with no KYC required for your users.\",\"builder_tracking_title\":\"Real-time order tracking\",\"builder_tracking_body\":\"Streaming status updates from payment to delivery, with polling fallback.\",\"how_it_works_quick_start\":\"Quick-start\",\"how_it_works_title\":\"How it works\",\"how_it_works_subtitle\":\"Take a user from discovery to delivered gift card.\",\"how_it_works_step_1_title\":\"Search\",\"how_it_works_step_1_body\":\"Browse brands and products available in the user’s country.\",\"how_it_works_step_2_title\":\"Quote\",\"how_it_works_step_2_body\":\"Get the exact crypto amount for a denomination, coin, and network.\",\"how_it_works_step_3_title\":\"Pay\",\"how_it_works_step_3_body\":\"Create the order and receive a wallet address and coin amount.\",\"how_it_works_step_4_title\":\"Deliver\",\"how_it_works_step_4_body\":\"Stream or poll the order until it is Done, then return the code.\",\"zero_cost_no_label\":\"No\",\"zero_cost_item_prefunding\":\"prefunding\",\"zero_cost_item_startup_costs\":\"startup costs\",\"zero_cost_item_monthly_fees\":\"monthly fees\",\"zero_cost_tagline\":\"Start building today, you only pay per successful order.\"},\"ApiDocsDevelopers\":{\"title\":\"Cryptorefills developer API reference: Stablecoin checkout integration\",\"description\":\"Production-focused cURL and Node examples for Cryptorefills stablecoin checkout, order creation, and delivery tracking.\",\"header_badge\":\"API Scope\",\"header_title\":\"Developer API reference\",\"header_subtitle\":\"Production-focused cURL and Node examples for stablecoin checkout, order creation, and delivery tracking.\",\"header_covered_title\":\"Covered in this guide\",\"header_covered_item_1\":\"Gift cards\",\"header_covered_item_2\":\"Mobile top-ups\",\"header_covered_item_3\":\"eSIM purchases\",\"header_not_covered_title\":\"Not covered here\",\"header_not_covered_item_1\":\"Flights\",\"header_not_covered_item_2\":\"Stays\",\"header_need_context\":\"Need the broader integration context before diving into endpoints?\",\"header_open_overview\":\"Open integration overview\",\"sidebar_authentication\":\"Authentication\",\"sidebar_headers\":\"Headers\",\"sidebar_payment_methods\":\"Payment methods\",\"sidebar_brand_catalog\":\"Brand catalog\",\"sidebar_homepage_feed\":\"Homepage feed\",\"sidebar_browse_products\":\"Browse products\",\"sidebar_get_crypto_price\":\"Get crypto price\",\"sidebar_validate_order\":\"Validate order\",\"sidebar_create_order\":\"Create order\",\"sidebar_track_order_stream\":\"Track order (stream API)\",\"sidebar_track_order_polling\":\"Track order (polling)\",\"section_authentication_title\":\"Authentication\",\"auth_partner_id\":\"Partner ID\",\"auth_partner_id_load_error\":\"Unable to load partner ID information\",\"auth_partner_id_use_prefix\":\"Use this value as\",\"auth_partner_id_use_suffix\":\"in API requests.\",\"auth_not_logged_in_description\":\"Every API request requires these headers. After creating a Cryptorefills account, you can find your Partner ID on your account information page.\",\"auth_open_account_info\":\"Open your account information page\",\"section_payment_methods_title\":\"Payment methods\",\"section_payment_methods_description\":\"Fetch all supported coins and blockchain networks. Returns USDC, USDT on Solana, Ethereum, Base, Arbitrum, Polygon, and more.\",\"section_payment_methods_recommended\":\"Recommended:\",\"section_payment_methods_recommended_text\":\"USDC on Solana offers the lowest fees and fastest settlement.\",\"section_brand_catalog_title\":\"Brand catalog\",\"section_brand_catalog_description\":\"(Optional) List all available brands for a country. Great for building brand directory or search features.\",\"section_brand_catalog_countries_title\":\"Supported country codes\",\"section_brand_catalog_countries_search\":\"Search country or code\",\"section_brand_catalog_countries_empty\":\"No countries match your search.\",\"section_brand_catalog_logo_variants_title\":\"Logo URL variants\",\"section_brand_catalog_logo_variants_description\":\"Each brand returns a logo_url (default) and a logo_base_url. Append a suffix to logo_base_url to fetch optimized sizes and formats.\",\"section_brand_catalog_logo_variants_recommended\":\"Recommended\",\"section_brand_catalog_logo_variants_example_label\":\"Example:\",\"section_homepage_feed_title\":\"Homepage feed\",\"section_homepage_feed_description\":\"(Optional) Fetch a curated homepage feed for a country. Useful for displaying trending or featured gift cards.\",\"section_browse_products_title\":\"Browse products\",\"section_browse_products_description\":\"List all available gift cards for a brand and country. Supports fixed denominations and custom amounts (ranges).\",\"section_get_crypto_price_title\":\"Get crypto price\",\"section_get_crypto_price_description\":\"Convert any gift card value to stablecoin amount. Use this to show users the exact crypto amount before they confirm purchase.\",\"section_validate_order_title\":\"Validate order\",\"section_validate_order_description\":\"(Recommended) Check for issues before creating the order. Use the real end-user email in email/beneficiary_account, since Cryptorefills delivers to that recipient.\",\"section_validate_order_errors_title\":\"Possible errors\",\"section_validate_order_errors_intro\":\"The response returns a problems array. Each entry has the shape '{' problem, moreDetails? '}', and multiple problems can be returned at once. Top-level HTTP errors (suspensions) come back as '{' status, detail, moreDetails? '}' instead.\",\"section_create_order_title\":\"Create order\",\"section_create_order_description\":\"Create an order and receive a wallet address for payment. Use the real end-user email because Cryptorefills must deliver the product to that recipient. Payment window is 30 minutes.\",\"section_create_order_abuse_title\":\"Only create orders your users intend to pay\",\"section_create_order_abuse_body_1_prefix\":\"Don't create orders to test your integration, check pricing, or validate input. That's what the\",\"section_create_order_abuse_body_1_link\":\"validate order\",\"section_create_order_abuse_body_1_suffix\":\"endpoint is for — it runs the same product, limit, and compliance checks without ever generating an order.\",\"section_create_order_abuse_body_2\":\"Every created order counts against your partner key. A high ratio of orders that are created but never paid is treated as abuse and can trigger automatic rate limiting and temporary suspension of your key.\",\"section_create_order_abuse_cta\":\"Use validate order for testing and dry runs\",\"section_create_order_response_includes\":\"Response includes\",\"section_create_order_share_with_user\":\"Share these with your user.\",\"section_create_order_beneficiary_title\":\"Beneficiary account\",\"section_create_order_beneficiary_intro_prefix\":\"Each delivery must include a\",\"section_create_order_beneficiary_intro_suffix\":\"in its deliverable that's where Cryptorefills delivers the product. The required format depends on the product kind.\",\"section_create_order_beneficiary_giftcard_esim_label\":\"Gift cards and eSIMs:\",\"section_create_order_beneficiary_giftcard_esim_body\":\"use the end-user's email address — for example\",\"section_create_order_beneficiary_mobile_topup_label\":\"Mobile topups:\",\"section_create_order_beneficiary_mobile_topup_body\":\"use the recipient's phone number in E.164 format, including the leading + and the country code — for example\",\"section_track_order_stream_title\":\"Track order (stream API)\",\"section_track_order_stream_description\":\"Implement this in two required pieces: a server-side SSE proxy route and a client-side stream hook.\",\"section_track_order_stream_item_1_prefix\":\"API route receives\",\"section_track_order_stream_item_1_middle\":\"and forwards to upstream\",\"section_track_order_stream_item_2_prefix\":\"Client hook opens\",\"section_track_order_stream_item_2_suffix\":\"to the local API route, validates payloads, and reconnects with backoff when needed.\",\"section_track_order_stream_server_code\":\"Server-Side Essential Code\",\"section_track_order_stream_client_code\":\"Client-Side Essential Code\",\"section_track_order_stream_route_in_repo\":\"Route in this repo\",\"section_track_order_stream_server_side\":\"Server side (API route)\",\"section_track_order_stream_server_text_prefix\":\"Uses session-based server headers via\",\"section_track_order_stream_server_text_middle\":\", then calls upstream\",\"section_track_order_stream_server_text_suffix\":\"On connection failure it returns\",\"section_track_order_stream_client_side\":\"Client side (hook)\",\"section_track_order_stream_client_text_prefix\":\"Opens\",\"section_track_order_stream_client_text_middle_1\":\"to\",\"section_track_order_stream_client_text_middle_2\":\"validates each payload with\",\"section_track_order_stream_client_text_middle_3\":\"handles\",\"section_track_order_stream_client_text_suffix\":\"events, and reconnects with exponential backoff.\",\"section_track_order_polling_title\":\"Track order (polling)\",\"section_track_order_polling_description\":\"Fallback approach: poll every 5-10 seconds until payment is received. Gift card code appears when status is 'Done'.\",\"section_track_order_polling_use_when\":\"Use polling when\",\"section_track_order_polling_use_when_text\":\"You cannot keep an SSE connection open, or your client environment does not support EventSource reliably.\",\"section_track_order_polling_states\":\"Typical order states\",\"section_track_order_polling_states_text\":\"WaitingForPayment -\u003e WaitingForDelivery -\u003e Done\"},\"Promotions\":{\"amazon_prime_day_badge\":\"Amazon Prime Day 2026\",\"amazon_prime_day_title\":\"Prime Day is almost here!\",\"amazon_prime_day_subtitle\":\"July 8, 2026 - Buy Amazon gift cards with crypto\",\"days\":\"Days\",\"hours\":\"Hours\",\"minutes\":\"Minutes\",\"seconds\":\"Seconds\",\"buy_now\":\"Buy now\",\"region\":\"{countries} only\",\"discount\":\"{percentage} OFF\",\"lastminute_subtext\":\"Redeem it for flights and hotels on lastminute.com.\"},\"Regions\":{\"global\":\"Global\",\"asia\":\"Asia\",\"europe\":\"Europe\"},\"CryptoUseMap\":{\"title\":\"Use Map — How Real People Use Crypto Every Day | Cryptorefills\",\"description\":\"Profiles of crypto users from 180+ countries documenting everyday USDT, BTC, and stablecoin spending on subscriptions, mobile top-ups, and international travel via Cryptorefills.\",\"hero_title\":\"How real people \u003chighlight\u003euse\u003c/highlight\u003e crypto every day\",\"hero_subtitle\":\"This map documents individuals across 180+ countries who have integrated stablecoins, Bitcoin, and other cryptocurrencies into routine transactions, covering software subscriptions, mobile top-ups, cross-border freelance payments, and international travel.\",\"cta_view_map\":\"View the map\",\"cta_browse_products\":\"Browse products\",\"stat_countries_supported\":\"Countries supported\",\"stat_featured_stories\":\"Featured stories\",\"stat_most_used_stablecoin\":\"Most used stablecoin\",\"section_map_view\":\"Map view\",\"section_all_stories\":\"All stories\",\"filter_all\":\"All\",\"story_read\":\"Read story\",\"story_shop\":\"Shop products\",\"show_more\":\"Show more ({count} more stories)\",\"no_stories_match\":\"No stories match this filter.\",\"popup_read_full_story\":\"Read the full story\",\"legend_africa\":\"Africa\",\"legend_europe\":\"Europe\",\"legend_asia\":\"Asia\",\"legend_americas\":\"Americas\",\"donut_crypto_label\":\"crypto\",\"map_aria_label\":\"World map of people using crypto around the world\",\"close\":\"Close\"},\"Points\":{\"title\":\"Points - Cryptorefills\",\"rewards\":\"Points\",\"redeem_your_cryptorefills_points_for_crypto\":\"Redeem your Cryptorefills points for crypto\",\"points_earned\":\"Points earned\",\"your_cryptorefills_points_will_become_available_in_48_hours_after_your_purchase\":\"Your Cryptorefills points will become available in 48 hours after your purchase\",\"we_re_currently_performing_maintenance_to_improve\":\"We’re currently performing maintenance to improve your experience. The redeem page is temporarily unavailable, but we’ll be back shortly. Thank you for your patience.\",\"redeem_history\":\"Redeem history\",\"no_redeem_history\":\"No redemption history available\",\"cost\":\"Cost\",\"available_points\":\"Available points\",\"points_label\":\"points\",\"level_up_your_points\":\"Level up your points\",\"share_your_referral_link_to_earn_more_cryptorefills_points\":\"Share your referral link to earn more Cryptorefills points.\",\"reward_catalog\":\"Reward catalog\",\"redeem_your_cryptorefills_points_for_crypto_vouchers\":\"Redeem your Cryptorefills points for crypto vouchers.\",\"activity\":\"Activity\",\"no_activity_yet\":\"No activity yet.\",\"status_pending\":\"pending\",\"status_cancelled\":\"cancelled\",\"loyalty_heading\":\"Cryptorefills points\",\"loyalty_subtitle\":\"Your points balance and activity.\",\"available_to_spend\":\"Available to spend\",\"points_earned_all_time\":\"{count, number} points earned all-time\",\"no_points_yet\":\"You haven’t earned any points yet.\",\"reserved\":\"Reserved\",\"reserved_hint\":\"Held for a pending order.\",\"reserved_info_label\":\"What reserved means\",\"locked\":\"Locked\",\"locked_hint\":\"Earned but not yet spendable. These points unlock a few days after you earn them.\",\"locked_info_label\":\"What locked means\",\"spent\":\"Spent\",\"points_expire_on\":\"{count, number} points expire on {date}\",\"points_unlock_on\":\"{count, number} points unlock on {date}\",\"balance_load_error\":\"Couldn’t load your balance. Refresh to try again.\",\"history\":\"History\",\"activity_load_error\":\"Couldn’t load your activity.\",\"retry\":\"Retry\",\"column_date\":\"Date\",\"column_expires\":\"Expires\",\"column_points\":\"Points\",\"copy_order_id\":\"Copy order id\",\"tx_order\":\"Order {orderId}\",\"tx_kyc_reward\":\"Identity verification reward\",\"tx_migration\":\"Migrated from previous programme\",\"tx_points_added\":\"Points added\",\"tx_points_removed\":\"Points removed\",\"tx_points_activity\":\"Points activity\",\"migration_notice_title\":\"A new way to use your points is coming\",\"migration_notice_body\":\"We’re upgrading our loyalty programme. Soon you’ll be able to spend points directly on your orders at checkout. No vouchers, no extra steps. While we migrate, redeeming points for crypto vouchers is paused. Your balance is safe and carries over.\"},\"BrandIdentity\":{\"downloadButton\":\"Download brand kit\",\"hero\":{\"titleLead\":\"Cryptorefills\",\"titleHighlight\":\"brand identity\",\"intro\":\"The marks, colours and type that make Cryptorefills recognisable, and the thinking behind each choice. The logo files are in the brand kit below; the colour and type live on this page.\"},\"logo\":{\"title\":\"Logo\",\"lede\":\"The wordmark does the work; the standalone icon steps in where space is tight, like avatars and app tiles. Both stay a single colour on purpose, so the mark reads cleanly on any background, light or dark.\"},\"usage\":{\"title\":\"Using the logo.\",\"clarification\":\"room to breathe, plus a few rules\",\"lede\":\"The mark earns its trust by being used consistently. Give it room to breathe first, then a handful of rules, each shown both ways.\",\"doLabel\":\"Do\",\"dontLabel\":\"Don't\",\"clearSpaceLabel\":\"Clear space\",\"clearSpaceUnit\":\"= clear space\",\"clearSpaceBody\":\"The icon is the unit: keep at least one of it as clear space on every side, and never let type, edges or other logos cross into that zone. Because the unit is the mark itself, the spacing scales with the logo at any size.\",\"rules\":{\"oneColour\":{\"topic\":\"One colour\",\"do\":\"Use a single brand colour: navy on light, white on dark.\",\"dont\":\"Recolour it outside the palette, or add gradients.\"},\"proportions\":{\"topic\":\"Proportions\",\"do\":\"Scale it evenly, and keep it upright.\",\"dont\":\"Stretch, squash or rotate the mark.\"},\"minimumSize\":{\"topic\":\"Minimum size\",\"do\":\"Keep the wordmark at least 24px tall on screen, 6mm in print, so the letterforms stay crisp.\",\"dont\":\"Shrink it past the point the wordmark stops holding together.\"},\"surface\":{\"topic\":\"Surface\",\"do\":\"Place it on a solid surface with enough contrast to stay legible.\",\"dont\":\"Add shadows or glows, or set it on a busy photo.\"}}},\"colour\":{\"title\":\"Colour\",\"lede\":\"The brand runs on one navy scale, a set of neutrals and four signal colours. Most of the interface stays quiet and lets the words lead; the navy carries the moments that matter.\",\"navyTitle\":\"Built on a single navy\",\"navyBody\":\"Deep Ocean Navy is the anchor. We keep it for the moments that should feel committed: the hero, a confirmed payment, the button we actually want pressed.\",\"navySwatch\":\"Deep Ocean Navy · #001588\",\"neutralTitle\":\"Neutral surface\",\"neutralBody\":\"Where the words earn the read.\",\"signalsBody\":\"Four signal colours. They flag a state and nothing else, never decoration.\"},\"type\":{\"title\":\"Typography\",\"lede\":\"Cryptorefills sets its type in the system typeface your device already uses. A deliberate choice, not a fallback: the brand should feel native wherever it appears, the same on a phone, a terminal or a partner's deck. Fira Code carries the technical detail.\",\"sansSpecimen\":\"The blockchain gateway to the real world.\",\"monoCaption\":\"Addresses, amounts and transaction IDs\"},\"kit\":{\"title\":\"Brand kit.\",\"clarification\":\"the logo, in every format\",\"cardTitle\":\"Everything in one download\",\"cardBody\":\"Every logo file you need for print and screen, packaged and ready to drop into place.\",\"format\":\"ZIP archive\",\"contact\":\"Questions about using the brand?\"}},\"RegionsByIsoCode\":{\"ww\":\"Global\",\"asia\":\"Asia\",\"eu\":\"Europe\"},\"Countr